%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Streamy%20Awards%202023%20Scores%20Record-Breaking%2015%20Million%20Views%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693457387000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGettyImages-1643342425.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235709090%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202023%20Streamy%20Awards%20amassed%2015%20million%20views%20across%20all%20digital%20platforms%20in%20its%20first%2048%20hours%2C%20setting%20a%20record%20as%20the%20most%20watched%20show%20in%20the%20event%E2%80%99s%2013-year%20history.%20The%20awards%20ceremony%20took%20place%20on%20Aug.%2027%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20This%20year%E2%80%99s%20Streamy%20Awards%2C%20hosted%20by%20YouTube%20star%20MatPat%2C%20broke%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%202021%20record%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Michaela%20Zee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fdigital%2Fnews%2Fstreamy-awards-2023-views-sets-record-1235709090%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fdigital%2Fnews%2Fstreamy-awards-2023-views-sets-record-1235709090%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fdigital%2Fnews%2Fstreamy-awards-2023-views-sets-record-1235709090%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Updates%3A%20Fresh%20Injuries%2C%20CBI%20Takes%20Over%2027%20Cases%2C%20Meira%20Paibis%20Against%20Assam%20Rifles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31100847%2FF4tkKVqaYAAQQFq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fresh%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20led%20to%20injuries%20in%20two%20security%20forces%20fighters%20and%20five%20civilians%20near%20Naransena%20village%20in%20Bishnupur%20district%2C%20where%20a%20gunfight%20has%20continued%20for%20over%2036%20hours%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-fresh-violence-erupts-in-churachandpur-one-person-from-the-kuki-zo-community-dies%5C%22%3ETwo%20days%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20areas%20adjoining%20the%20village%2C%20two%20men%20had%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Farmed-miscreants-from-kuki-and-meitei-communities-engage-in-firing-injuring-seven-in-manipur-s-ethnic-strife-101693420453672.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20firing%20between%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20groups%20started%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20August%2029%20after%20a%2026-year-old%20farmer%2C%20Salam%20Jotin%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Naransena%2C%20was%20shot%20at%20by%20miscreants.%20He%20sustained%20a%20bullet%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnnamed%20officials%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20two%20battalions%20of%20the%20India%20Reserve%20Battalion%2C%20a%20special%20armed%20force%20of%20the%20state%2C%20were%20deployed%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20two%20jawans%20from%20among%20them%20who%20received%20injuries%20are%20recovering%2C%20as%20are%20the%20five%20civilians%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firing%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20stopped%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI%20takes%20over%2027%20FIRs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20has%20taken%20over%20cases%20pertaining%20to%2027%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20thus%20registered%2027%20corresponding%20cases%2C%20out%20of%20which%2019%20are%20of%20crime%20against%20women%2C%20three%20pertain%20to%20an%20armory%20loot%20by%20a%20mob%2C%20two%20are%20of%20murder%20and%20one%20each%20of%20rioting%20and%20murder%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20general%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20agency%20report%20said%2C%20quoting%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBI%20team%20of%2053%20officers%2C%20of%20whom%2029%20are%20women%2C%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20Manipur%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20who%20spoke%20to%20PTI%20said%20the%20investigators%20were%20keen%20to%20avoid%20allegations%20of%20bias%20while%20looking%20into%20the%20ethnic%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20said%20several%20of%20these%20cases%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20CBI%20may%20attract%20provisions%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20which%20can%20be%20probed%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeira%20Paibis%20versus%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20fissures%20between%20the%20Meitei%20women%20activists%20called%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20the%20paramilitary%20force%20Assam%20Rifles%20grows%2C%20with%20the%20former%20reviving%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20removal%20from%20strife-torn%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fmeitei-women-revive-demand-for-removal-of-assam-rifles-from-strife-torn-manipur%2Fcid%2F1962709%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20representatives%20of%20the%20Committee%20on%20Mass%20Protest%20Against%20Assam%20Rifles%20called%20on%20governor%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2030.%20The%20group%20reminded%20the%20government%20of%20their%20August%209%20memorandum%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20through%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20in%20the%20delegation%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20they%20asked%20the%20governor%20what%20the%20status%20of%20their%20memorandum%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20said%20she%20had%20discussed%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20would%20discuss%20it%20again.%20We%20want%20their%20removal%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECPI(M)%20delegation%20finds%20state%20deeply%20divided%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CPI(M)%20central%20committee%20delegation%20of%20party%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20along%20with%20Jitendera%20Choudhury%2C%20Debolina%20Hembram%20and%20Suprakash%20Talukdar%2C%20that%20visited%20the%20state%20from%20August%2018-20%2C%20found%20the%20stage%20deeply%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20segregation%20is%20stark%3A%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%20no%20longer%20houses%20anyone%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20even%20government%20officials%20who%E2%80%99ve%20moved%20to%20Kuki-Zo%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20on%20the%20party%20paper%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20visited%20the%20Saithong%20Relief%20camp%20in%20Moirang%2C%20where%20370%20Meitei%20individuals%20sought%20refuge%20since%20May%204.%20After%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20relief%20distribution%20effort%2C%20the%20delegation%20proceeded%20to%20Churachandpur%20district%20and%20visited%20two%20relief%20camps%20at%20Koite%20with%20200%20Kuki-Zo%20residents%20and%20another%20at%20Saidan.%20This%20camp%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20accommodated%20Hmar%20and%20Thadao%20speakers%20who%20fled%20Sangang%20and%20Lanja%20villages%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20also%20met%20religious%20heads%20like%20Archbishop%20Dominic%20Luman%2C%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20like%20Churachandpur%E2%80%99s%20DC%20and%20SP%2C%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Governor%2C%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%2C%20and%20with%C2%A0Churachandpur%E2%80%99s%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20prominent%20individuals%20at%20the%20Kuki%20INPT%20office%20in%20Tuibong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693456841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31100847%2FF4tkKVqaYAAQQFq.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-firing-cbi-meira-paibis-cpim-delegation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20firing%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20near%20Naransena%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20stopped%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-firing-cbi-meira-paibis-cpim-delegation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Rejects%20%26quot%3BRecycled%20Allegations%26quot%3B%20In%20OCCRP%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20today%20categorically%20rejected%20allegations%20of%20hidden%20foreign%20investors%20in%20a%20report%20by%20the%20George%20Soros-owned%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20categorically%20reject%20these%20recycled%20allegations.%20These%20news%20reports%20appear%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20meritless%20Hindenburg%20report.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20was%20anticipated%2C%20as%20was%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20independent%20adjudicating%20authority%20and%20an%20appellate%20tribunal%20had%20both%20confirmed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20over-valuation%20and%20that%20the%20transactions%20were%20in%20accordance%20with%20applicable%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20vital%20to%20respect%20the%20ongoing%20regulatory%20process%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20are%20both%20overseeing%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20complete%20faith%20in%20the%20due%20process%20of%20law%20and%20remain%20confident%20of%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20disclosures%20and%20corporate%20governance%20standards.%20In%20light%20of%20these%20facts%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20these%20news%20reports%20is%20suspicious%2C%20mischievous%20and%20malicious%20-%20and%20we%20reject%20these%20reports%20in%20their%20entirety%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20attained%20finality%20in%20March%202023%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20ruled%20in%20our%20favour.%20Clearly%2C%20since%20there%20was%20no%20over-valuation%2C%20there%20is%20no%20relevance%20or%20foundation%20for%20these%20allegations%20on%20transfer%20of%20funds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company%2C%20the%20claims%20were%20based%20on%20closed%20cases%20from%20a%20decade%20ago%20when%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20probed%20allegations%20of%20over%20invoicing%2C%20transfer%20of%20funds%20abroad%2C%20related%20party%20transactions%20and%20investments%20through%20FPIs%20(Foreign%20Portfolio%20Investment).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNotably%2C%20these%20FPIs%20are%20already%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20SEBI.%20As%20per%20the%20Expert%20Committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20breach%20of%20the%20Minimum%20Public%20Shareholding%20(MPS)%20requirements%20or%20manipulation%20of%20stock%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20these%20publications%2C%20which%20sent%20us%20queries%2C%20chose%20not%20to%20carry%20our%20response%20in%20full.%20These%20attempts%20are%20aimed%20at%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20generating%20profits%20by%20driving%20down%20our%20stock%20prices%20and%20these%20short%20sellers%20are%20under%20investigation%20by%20various%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20port-to-energy%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693456800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fbhp1gurg_adani-group_625x300_19_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-rejects-allegations-of-hidden-foreign-investors-by-george-soros-funded-occrp-calls-them-recycled-allegations-4344117%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Adani%20Group%20today%20categorically%20rejected%20allegations%20of%20hidden%20foreign%20investors%20in%20a%20report%20by%20the%20George%20Soros-owned%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-rejects-allegations-of-hidden-foreign-investors-by-george-soros-funded-occrp-calls-them-recycled-allegations-4344117%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-rejects-allegations-of-hidden-foreign-investors-by-george-soros-funded-occrp-calls-them-recycled-allegations-4344117%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-rejects-allegations-of-hidden-foreign-investors-by-george-soros-funded-occrp-calls-them-recycled-allegations-4344117%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Warns%20Of%20Fake%20Website%20Stealing%20User%20Details%2C%20Card%20Information%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sign%20that%20no%20person%20or%20institution%20is%20too%20big%20for%20scamsters%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20being%20misused%20to%20steal%20people's%20personal%20details%20and%20confidential%20data.%20The%20registry%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20and%20warned%20people%20about%20the%20scam.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registry%20said%20it%20has%20been%20made%20aware%20of%20a%20phishing%20attack%20in%20which%20a%20fake%20website%2C%20impersonating%20the%20official%20Supreme%20Court%20website%2C%20has%20been%20created%20and%20hosted%20on%20the%20URLs%20http%3A%2F%2Fcbins%2Fscigv.com%20and%20https%3A%2F%2Fcbins.scigv.com%2Foffence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20URL%2C%20which%20has%20the%20header%20'Offence%20of%20Money-Laundering'%20is%20being%20used%20to%20steal%20people's%20personal%20details%2C%C2%A0internet-banking%20and%20credit%20and%20debit%20card%20information%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official-looking%20website%20details%20the%20offence%20and%20then%20has%20space%20for%20the%20user%20to%20fill%20in%20various%20boxes%2C%20including%20bank%20name%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20permanent%20account%20number%20(PAN)%20'online%20banking%20user%20ID'%2C%20'log-in%20password'%20and%20'card%20password%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20visitor%20on%20the%20above%20URLs%20is%20strongly%20advised%20not%20to%20share%20and%20divulge%20any%20personal%20and%20confidential%20information%2C%20as%20the%20same%20shall%20enable%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20steal%20the%20information.%20Please%20note%20that%20the%20Registry%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20will%20never%20ask%20for%20personal%20information%2C%20financial%20details%20or%20other%20confidential%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registry%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20flagged%20the%20phishing%20attack%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20so%20that%20they%20can%20investigate%20it%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20justice%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India's%20official%20domain%20is%20www.sci.gov.in%20and%20asked%20people%20to%20verify%20URLs%20before%20clicking%20on%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20you%20have%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20above%20phishing%20attack%2C%20please%20change%20your%20passwords%20for%20all%20your%20online%20accounts%20and%20also%20contact%20your%20bank%20and%20credit%20card%20company%20to%20report%20such%20unauthorised%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693456500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-warns-of-fake-website-stealing-user-details-card-information-4344116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sign%20that%20no%20person%20or%20institution%20is%20too%20big%20for%20scamsters%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20being%20misused%20to%20steal%20people's%20personal%20details%20and%20confidential%20data.%20The%20registry%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-warns-of-fake-website-stealing-user-details-card-information-4344116%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-warns-of-fake-website-stealing-user-details-card-information-4344116%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-warns-of-fake-website-stealing-user-details-card-information-4344116%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All-new%20Hero%20Karizma%20tested%3A%20Nothing%20like%20the%20old%20model%20but%20better%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693455980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103230930%2Cimgsize-1768550.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Freviews%2Fhero-karizma-xmr-review-nothing-like-the-old-model-but-better-than-new-rivals%2Farticleshow%2F103230181.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20soon%20as%20you%20swing%20your%20leg%20over%20the%20Karizma%20and%20take%20a%20seat%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20you%20will%20realise%20is%20how%20light%20the%20motorcycle%20is.%20The%20next%20big%