A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F31%2Fmodi-linked-adani-family-secretly-invested-in-own-shares-documents-suggest-india%5C%22%3Ewrites%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Coffshore%20financial%20records%20seen%20by%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F8d46b435-9725-46d4-80be-2cb3e276c4c9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20two%20men%20were%20using%20one%20Global%20Opportunities%20Fund%20in%20Bermuda%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20a%20specific%20purpose%20%E2%80%94%20to%20amass%20and%20trade%20large%20positions%20in%20shares%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20politically%20connected%20private%20conglomerates%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20FT%20concludes%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20men%20%E2%80%94%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20from%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20from%20Taiwan%E2%80%9D%2C%20associates%20of%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20brother%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20founder%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20had%20their%20investments%20%E2%80%9Coverseen%20by%20a%20Vinod%20Adani%20employee%2C%20raising%20questions%20over%20whether%20they%20were%20front%20men%20used%20to%20bypass%20rules%20for%20Indian%20companies%20that%20prevent%20share%20price%20manipulation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20potentially%20controversial%20owners%20of%20Adani%20stock%20have%20been%20identified%20since%20the%20American%20short%20selling%20firm%20Hindenburg%20Research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%20an%20explosive%20report%20in%20January%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20accused%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20running%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%E2%80%9D%2C%20writes%20FT.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2FInvetsors%2FAdani-Response-to-Hindenburg-January-29-2023.pdf%5C%22%3EAdani%20had%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20trail%20and%20documents%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Ebeen%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20or%20OCCRP%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20network%20of%20investigative%20journalists%2C%20which%20put%20out%20its%20story%20on%20the%20specific%20route%20and%20method%20for%20investments%20in%20offshore%20companies%20early%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20writes%20that%20exclusive%20documents%20obtained%20by%20OCCRP%20and%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20it%20says%20were%20corroborated%20by%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20business%20and%20public%20records%20from%20multiple%20countries%2C%20%E2%80%9Cshow%20how%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20were%20invested%20in%20publicly%20traded%20Adani%20stock%20through%20opaque%20investment%20funds%20based%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20of%20Mauritius%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20writes%20that%20documents%20obtained%20by%20its%20reporters%20reveal%20how%20investments%20were%20flowing%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20involving%20two%20of%20the%2013%20offshore%20entities%20cited%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20Report%2C%20which%20were%20%E2%80%9Ca%20pair%20of%20Mauritius-based%20investment%20funds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20funds%2C%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Fund%20(EIFF)%20and%20EM%20Resurgent%20Fund%20(EMRF)%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20typical%20offshore%20investment%20vehicles%2C%20operated%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20number%20of%20wealthy%20investors.%20But%20documents%20obtained%20by%20reporters%20show%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20large%20percentage%20of%20the%20money%20was%20placed%20into%20these%20funds%20by%20two%20foreign%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20Chang%20from%20Taiwan%20and%20Ahli%20from%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20%E2%80%94%20who%20used%20them%20to%20trade%20large%20amounts%20of%20shares%20in%20four%20Adani%20companies%20between%202013%20and%202018%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%20March%202017%2C%20as%20per%20OCCRP%2C%20the%20value%20of%20the%20investments%20in%20Adani%20Group%20stock%20was%20%24430%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20followed%20a%20convoluted%20trail%2C%20making%20it%20exceedingly%20difficult%20to%20follow.%20It%20was%20channelled%20through%20four%20companies%3A%20Lingo%20Investment%20Ltd%20(BVI)%2C%20owned%20by%20Chang%3B%20Gulf%20Arij%20Trading%20FZE%20(UAE)%2C%20owned%20by%20Ahli%3B%20Mid%20East%20Ocean%20Trade%20(Mauritius)%2C%20of%20which%20Ahli%20was%20the%20beneficial%20owner%3B%20and%20Gulf%20Asia%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Investment%20Ltd%20(BVI)%2C%20of%20which%20Ahli%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontrolling%20person%E2%80%9D)%20and%20the%20Bermuda-based%20fund%2C%20the%20Global%20Opportunities%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20writes%20that%20fund%20managers%20in%20charge%20of%20Chang%20and%20Ahli%E2%80%99s%20investments%20in%20EIFF%20and%20EMRF%20%E2%80%9Creceived%20direct%20instructions%20on%20the%20investments%20from%20an%20Adani%20company.%E2%80%9D%20It%20says%20%E2%80%9Can%20agreement%20for%20Excel%20to%20provide%20advisory%20services%20to%20EIFF%20and%20EMRF%20was%20signed%20for%20Excel%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20himself%20in%202011%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20documents%20obtained%20by%20OCCRP%2C%20these%20investments%20resulted%20in%20significant%20profits%2C%20netting%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20over%20the%20years%20as%20EIFF%20and%20EMRF%20repeatedly%20bought%20Adani%20stock%20low%20and%20sold%20it%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20them%2C%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20investment%20in%20June%202016%2C%20the%20two%20funds%20held%20free-floating%20shares%20of%20four%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20ranging%20from%208%25%20to%20nearly%2014%25%3A%20Adani%20Power%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20Adani%20Ports%2C%20and%20Adani%20Transmissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChang%20and%20Ahli%E2%80%99s%20connections%20to%20the%20Adani%20family%20have%20been%20widely%20reported%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20men%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20family%20in%20two%20separate%20government%20investigations%20into%20alleged%20wrongdoing%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20Both%20cases%20were%20eventually%20dismissed%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20OCCRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResponse%20to%20charges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20writes%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Chang%20and%20Ahli%E2%80%99s%20money%20for%20their%20Adani%20Group%20investments%20came%20from%20the%20Adani%20family.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20source%20of%20the%20funds%20is%20unknown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20documents%20obtained%20by%20OCCRP%2C%20they%20claim%2C%20show%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20used%20one%20of%20the%20same%20Mauritius%20funds%20to%20make%20his%20own%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20told%20OCCRP%20that%20the%20Mauritius%20funds%20investigated%20by%20reporters%20had%20already%20been%20named%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindenburg%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20the%20short-seller%20that%20sparked%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20scandal.%20(The%20report%20did%20name%20these%20offshore%20companies%2C%20but%20did%20not%20reveal%20who%20was%20using%20them%20to%20make%20investments%20in%20Adani%20stock.)%20The%20Adani%20representative%20also%20cited%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20expert%20committee%2C%20which%20described%20a%20financial%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20matter%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20proved%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20these%20facts%2C%20these%20allegations%20are%20not%20only%20baseless%20and%20unsubstantiated%20but%20are%20rehashed%20from%20Hindenburg%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20representative%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20it%20is%20categorically%20stated%20that%20all%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20publicly%20listed%20entities%20are%20in%20compliance%20with%20all%20applicable%20laws%20including%20the%20regulation%20relating%20to%20public%20share%20holdings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comments%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chang%20said%20he%20knew%20nothing%20about%20any%20secret%20purchases%20of%20Adani%20stock.%20He%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20he%20had%20bought%20any%2C%20but%20asked%20why%20journalists%20were%20not%20interested%20in%20his%20other%20investments.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20simple%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20before%20ending%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Adani%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Though%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20denied%20that%20he%20has%20a%20role%20in%20running%20the%20conglomerate%2C%20it%20admitted%20this%20March%20that%20he%20was%20part%20of%20its%20%E2%80%9Cpromoter%20group%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20he%20had%20control%20over%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20company%20and%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20informed%20of%20all%20holdings%20in%20Adani%20Group%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-gautam-adani-u-turn%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%202023%2C%20on%20how%20the%20Adani%20group%20had%2C%20after%20first%20distancing%20itself%20from%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Vinod%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Vinod%20Adani%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20one%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20on%20Gudami%20International%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20company%20named%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%20as%20being%20an%20Adani%20group%20%E2%80%9Crelated%20party%E2%80%9D%20and%20one%20that%20figured%20in%20the%20first%20chargesheet%20and%20second%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20the%20AgustaWestland%20helicopter%20scam%2C%20but%20was%20then%20subsequently%20dropped%20in%20the%20third%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20in%202018%2C%20after%20authorities%20in%20Singapore%20replied%20to%20the%20Letter%20Rogatory%20(LR)%20sent%20to%20them%20by%20the%20ED.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhindenburg-spotlights-an-offshore-adani-related-entity-that-ed-had-linked-to-agustawestland-scam%5C%22%3EIts%20director%20was%20identified%20as%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20director%20in%20other%20Adani%20entities.%20As%20per%20the%20DRI%20probe%2C%20reported%20by%20Hindenburg%2C%20the%20registered%20office%20address%20of%20Adani%20Global%20Ltd%20(later%20the%20flagship%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd)%2C%20in%20Singapore%20was%20also%20the%20residential%20address%20of%20Chang%20Chung-Ling.%20Vinod%20Shantilal%20Shah%2C%20director%20of%20Adani%20Global%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20were%20shown%20to%20be%20residing%20at%20the%20same%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20reports%20were%20published%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20published%20a%20media%20statement%20in%20which%20it%20said%20these%20were%20%E2%80%9Crecycled%20allegations%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20news%20reports%20appear%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20meritless%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20allegations%20of%20OCCRP%2C%20Adani%20Group%20says%20%E2%80%9CWe%20categorically%20reject%20these%20recycled%20allegations.%20These%20news%20reports%20appear%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20meritless%20Hindenburg%20report.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhOfRU4BUSN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhOfRU4BUSN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1697103356379255126%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstitutional%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20under%20intense%20attack%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F02%2F16%2Fadanis-epic-fall-reignites-scrutiny-on-tycoons-close-ties-modi-.html%5C%22%3Eclose%20personal%20ties%20with%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20stopped%20public%20appearances%20with%20Adani%20since%20the%20Hindenburg%20Report%20in%20January%20termed%20the%20group%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20largest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20up%20an%20expert%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations.%20SEBI%20also%20was%20tasked%20to%20look%20into%20allegations%2C%20and%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fadani-group-probe-supreme-court-postpones-hearing-in-sebi-status-report-adani-hindenburg-396060-2023-08-29%5C%22%3Eon%20August%2025%2C%20it%20submitted%20its%20status%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI%20reported%20that%20SEBI%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20still%20awaiting%20information%20from%20five%20tax%20havens%20on%20actual%20owners%20behind%20foreign%20investors%20investi