0have%20the%20court%20resolve%20the%20case%20before%20it%20goes%20to%20trial%20based%20on%20the%20documents%20submitted%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20allege%20Trump%20overstated%20his%20wealth%20each%20year%20between%202011%20and%202021%2C%20including%20the%20years%20he%20was%20president%2C%20between%2017%20and%2039%20percent%20--%20amounting%20to%20%24812%20million%20and%20%242.2%20billion%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20undisputed%20evidence%2C%20no%20trial%20is%20required%20for%20the%20Court%20to%20determine%20that%20Defendants%20presented%20grossly%20and%20materially%20inflated%20asset%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20them%20conduct%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20transactions%20and%20defraud%20banks%20and%20insurers%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20was%20fined%20%241.6%20million%20by%20a%20New%20York%20judge%20in%20a%20criminal%20tax%20and%20financial%20fraud%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20James'%20civil%20case%20against%20Trump%20goes%20to%20trial%2C%20it%20will%20be%20one%20more%20for%20the%20candidate%20to%20have%20to%20juggle%20while%20also%20zipping%20across%20the%20country%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20facing%20four%20criminal%20trials%20for%20actions%20allegedly%20taken%20before%2C%20during%20and%20after%20his%20presidency%20--%20state%20cases%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Georgia%20and%20two%20federal%20cases%20in%20Florida%20and%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20in%20the%20past%20denounced%20the%20case%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwitch%20hunt%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20James%2C%20who%20is%20Black%2C%20%26quot%3Bracist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693455240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023