03%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fbest-pics-of-rare-super-blue-moon-from-around-the-world-4344103%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fbest-pics-of-rare-super-blue-moon-from-around-the-world-4344103%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20To%20Spell%20Out%20Timeframe%20To%20Restore%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Statehood%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20is%20likely%20to%20provide%20a%20timeframe%20on%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%2C%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20the%20state%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20will%20make%20a%20statement%20before%20a%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20is%20currently%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%20under%20which%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20had%20a%20special%20constitutional%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20had%20told%20the%20top%20court%20that%20he%20will%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20statement%26quot%3B%20on%20Thursday%20after%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20take%20instructions%20from%20the%20government%20and%20return%20with%20a%20timeframe%20for%20restoring%20the%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20taken%20instructions.%20The%20instructions%20are%20that%20Union%20Territory%20(of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20is%20not%20a%20permanent%20feature.%20I%20will%20make%20a%20positive%20statement%20the%20day%20after%20tomorrow.%20Ladakh%20will%20remain%20a%20UT%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Of%20India%2C%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20is%20conducting%20daily%20hearings%20of%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20last%20hearing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20the%20need%20to%20restore%20democracy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20has%20been%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20since%20June%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20you%20convert%20a%20State%20into%20a%20UT%3F%20And%20can%20a%20UT%20be%20carved%20out%20of%20a%20State.%20Also%2C%20when%20elections%20could%20be%20held%3F%20This%20has%20to%20come%20an%20end...%20give%20us%20the%20specific%20time%20frame%20as%20to%20when%20will%20you%20restore%20actual%20democracy.%20We%20want%20to%20record%20this%2C%20%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20told%20Mr%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20while%20acknowledging%20national%20security%20concerns%2C%20also%20insisted%20on%20restoration%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20has%20been%20directly%20administered%20by%20the%20central%20government%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20general%20and%20solicitor%20general%20are%20among%20the%20battery%20of%20senior%20lawyers%20who%20are%20defending%20Centre's%20decision%20while%20senior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20Gopal%20Subramanium%2C%20Rajeev%20Dhavan%20and%20several%20other%20top%20lawyers%20are%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20arguments%2C%20is%20if%20due%20process%20was%20followed%20while%20abrogating%20Article%20370%20and%20dividing%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories-%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20and%20petitioners%20from%20Ladakh%20have%20expressed%20their%20disappointment%20over%20The%20Solicitor%20General's%20statement%20that%20Ladakh%20will%20remain%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20there%20have%20been%20massive%20protests%20in%20Ladakh%20demanding%20statehood%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20scrapping%20Article%20370%20in%20August%202019%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20assured%20that%20it%20will%20restore%20statehood%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time.%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20reiterated%20the%20same%20but%20no%20deadline%20has%20been%20set%20for%20such%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693453680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2Fh0qapm6o_jammu-and-kashmir-police-generic-pti_625x300_11_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-spell-out-timeframe-to-restore-jammu-kashmir-statehood-today-4344053%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20is%20likely%20to%20provide%20a%20timeframe%20on%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%2C%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20the%20state%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-spell-out-timeframe-to-restore-jammu-kashmir-statehood-today-4344053%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-spell-out-timeframe-to-restore-jammu-kashmir-statehood-today-4344053%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-spell-out-timeframe-to-restore-jammu-kashmir-statehood-today-4344053%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20sees%20rare%20strike%20as%20workers%20at%20landmark%20department%20store%20protest%20sale%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693453588000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103230202%2Cimgsize-1641414.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-sees-rare-strike-as-workers-at-landmark-department-store-protest-sale%2Farticleshow%2F103229982.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103229982.cms%5C%22%20hspace