he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693450260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fqgn9vnq8_jasprit-bumrah-sanjana-ganesan-806_625x300_30_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fbhai-aaram-se-fans-concerned-as-jasprit-bumrah-plays-fifa-with-wife-sanjana-ganesan-4342654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20return%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20news%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20recent%20times%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fbhai-aaram-se-fans-concerned-as-jasprit-bumrah-plays-fifa-with-wife-sanjana-ganesan-4342654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fbhai-aaram-se-fans-concerned-as-jasprit-bumrah-plays-fifa-with-wife-sanjana-ganesan-4342654%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fbhai-aaram-se-fans-concerned-as-jasprit-bumrah-plays-fifa-with-wife-sanjana-ganesan-4342654%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Masked%20Robbers%20Pepper%20Spray%20US%20Jewelry%20Store%20Owner%20In%20%24500%2C000%20Heist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20three%20thieves%20armed%20with%20hammers%20conducted%20a%20bold%20smash-and-grab%20robbery%20at%20a%20California%20jewellery%20store.%20They%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20approximately%20%24500%2C000%20worth%20of%20jewellery%20in%20the%20daring%20robbery.%20The%20gang%20of%20criminals%20also%20assaulted%20the%20store%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fktla.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fsmash-and-grab-burglars-steal-over-500000-worth-of-jewelry-from-pasadena-shop%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKTLA%20News%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3ESam%20Babikian%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20'Jewels%20on%20Lake'%20in%20Pasadena%2C%20California%2C%20stated%20that%20three%20masked%20men%20wearing%20gloves