n.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20international%20travel%20is%20also%20helping%20boost%20Nevada's%20casino%20revenues%2C%20with%20more%20than%20290%2C000%20foreign%20tourists%20arriving%20and%20departing%20through%20the%20Harry%20Reid%20International%20Airport%20in%20July.%20That's%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20foreign%20travelers%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%20March%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solid%20month%20makes%20it%20increasingly%20likely%20that%20the%20state%20will%20experience%20a%20third%20straight%20year%20of%20record%20annual%20casino%20revenue.%20Nevada%20casinos%20generated%20gross%20gaming%20revenue%20of%20%2414.8%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20and%20%2413.4%20billion%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrength%20in%20the%20industry%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20broader%20signal%20to%20investors%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-economy-outlook-consumer-retail-spending-delinquencies-student-debt-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20economy%20is%20doing%20just%20fine%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20a%20potential%20recession%20is%20not%20on%20the%20horizon.%20That's%20because%20when%20consumers%20are%20feeling%20uneasy%20about%20their%20finances%2C%20they're%20less%20likely%20to%20book%20a%20trip%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20gamble%20their%20savings%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamed%20short-seller%20Jim%20Chanos%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjim-chanos-economy-recession-las-vegas-strip-party-casino-revenues-2023-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522Las%2520Vegas%2520Strip%2520revenue%2520has%2Cbefore%2520the%2520last%2520two%2520recessions.%2522%5C%22%3Esaid%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20casino%20revenue%20can%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20reliable%20data%20point%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLas%20Vegas%20Strip%20revenue%20has%20been%20a%20pretty%20good%20leading%2Fcoincident%20indicator%20of%20the%20US%20consumer.%2