ed%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20to%20discuss%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20will%20hear%20the%20state's%20plea%20to%20direct%20Karnataka%20to%20release%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20claiming%20that%20the%20Tribunal's%20order%20was%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20it%20was%20a%20normal%20monsoon%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20it%20was%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20said%20that%20the%20state%20cannot%20afford%20to%20release%20water%2C%20since%20it%20will%20empty%20the%20reservoirs%20and%20cause%20drinking%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20to%20meet%20our%20legal%20team.%20The%20hearing%20(on%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20plea%20on%20Cauvery%20water)%20will%20be%20coming%20on%20Friday.%20Our%20department%20officials%20have%20argued%20very%20well%20after%20Tamil%20Nadu%20demanded%2024-25%20TMC.%20We%20said%20we%20can%20give%203%2C000%20cusecs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20earlier%20today.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20discuss%20how%20much%20we%20can%20reduce%20(the%20water%20released%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu)%20by%20making%20the%20court%20understand%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20We%20don't%20want%20the%20keys%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20others.%20At%20present%2C%20the%20keys%20are%20with%20us%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20safeguard%20our%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDispute%20over%20Cauvery%20water%20between%20the%20two%20southern%20states%20has%20been%20on%20for%20decades.%20In%201990%2C%20the%20Centre%20formed%20the%20Cauvery%20Water%20Disputes%20Tribunal%20to%20adjudicate%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693419780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim