pathi-convicted-for-killing-poet-to-be-released-from-jail%5C%22%3ETripathi%E2%80%99s%20release%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20issued%2C%20she%20has%20been%20fearing%20for%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20August%2024%2C%20I%20have%20received%20six%20phone%20calls%20threatening%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20am%20very%20scared%2C%20as%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20long%20I%20will%20be%20alive.%20%3Cem%3EEk%20baar%20wo%20bahar%20aa%20jaye%2C%20mujhe%20chorega%20nahi.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BOnce%20he%20(Tripathi)%20comes%20out%2C%20he%20will%20not%20leave%20me%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%E2%80%99s%20wife%20was%20also%20convicted%20of%20murdering%2024-year-old%20Madhumita%20Shukla%2C%20who%20was%20seven%20months%20pregnant%20when%20she%20was%20killed%20in%20Lucknow%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPremature%20release%20citing%20%E2%80%98%20good%20behaviour%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20(August%2025)%2C%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition%20opposing%20the%20Tripathi%20couple%E2%80%99s%20premature%20release%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Flife-convicts-amarmani-tripathi-wife-released-after-16-years-in-up-jail%2Farticle67235749.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Supreme%2520Court%2520on%2520Friday%2Cmurder%2520of%2520poet%2520Madhumita%2520Shukla.%5C%22%3Eissued%20notices%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20Tripathi%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20while%20seeking%20their%20replies%20within%20eight%20weeks%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20stay%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Thursday%20(August%2024)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBenarasiyaa%2Fstatus%2F1694916061903389078%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Eordered%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20release%20of%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20were%20both%20serving%20life%20sentences%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20budding%20poet%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premature%20release%20was%20granted%20to%20them%2C%20citing%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%202018%20policy%20on%20remission%2C%20since%20they%20have%20completed%2016%20years%20of%20imprisonment%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnorth%2Flife-convicts-amarmani-tripathi-wife-set-to-be-released-after-16-years-in-up-jail%2F637036.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520prisons%2520department%2520had%2520on%2Ccompleted%252016%2520years%2520of%2520imprisonment.%5C%22%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prison%20department%20also%20cited%20their%20%E2%80%98old%20age%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98good%20behaviour%E2%80%99%20as%20Amarmani%20is%2066%20years%20old%20and%20Madhumani%20is%2061%2C%20Gorakhpur%20jail%20superintendent%20Dilip%20Pandey%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%209%2C%202003%2C%20Shukla%2C%20then%20a%20budding%20poet%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Paper%20Mill%20Colony.%20The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%E2%80%99s%20probe%20found%20that%20Tripathi%20and%20Shukla%20were%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20and%20a%20post-mortem%20report%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20seven%20months%20pregnant%20with%20his%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20minister%20tried%20to%20force%20her%20to%20have%20an%20abortion%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20failing%20which%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20hatched%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20the%20poet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202007%2C%20the%20Special%20CBI%20court%20in%20Dehradun%20sentenced%20the%20couple%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20along%20with%20two%20others%2C%20namely%20Rohit%20Chaturvedi%20(Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20nephew)%20and%20Santosh%20Kumar%20Rai%20(his%20close%20relative).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20high%20court%20in%20Nainital%20upheld%20the%20sentence.%20The%20case%20then%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20but%20no%20relief%20was%20granted%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202013%20also%20affirmed%20the%20life%20sentences%20handed%20out%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20H%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fright-wing-india-authoritarianism-psychological-warfare-old-ageing%5C%22%3Eow%20the%20Right%20Is%20Starting%20a%20Psychological%20War%20by%20Targeting%20the%20Old%20and%20Ageing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemission%20guidelines%20%E2%80%98overlooked%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20writ%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Nidhi%20Shukla%20opposed%20the%20UP%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20release%20the%20Tripathis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Esaid%20that%20the%20UP%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20overlooked%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-convicts-release-remission-policy-experts%5C%22%3Eguidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20grant%20of%20special%20remission%20to%20prisoners%20to%20commemorate%20the%20%E2%80%9C75th%20year%20of%20Independence%E2%80%9D%20that%20excluded%20those%20convicts%20who%20are%20serving%20life%20sentence%20for%20heinous%20offences%20from%20the%20purview%20of%20consideration%20even%20after%20the%20completion%20of%2014%20years%20of%20their%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20following%20the%20death%20of%20the%20then%2024-year-old%20poet%2C%20the%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20involvement%20and%20interference%20of%20a%20powerful%20politician%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmarmani%20Tripathi%20has%20been%20a%20four-time%20MLA%20in%20UP%20and%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20all%20four%20major%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Bahujan%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20won%20his%20last%20election%20in%202007%20while%20he%20was%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20murder%2C%20he%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20BSP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20and%20was%20sacked%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20while%20he%20had%20been%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Nautanwa%20constituency%2C%20Tripathi%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20influence%E2%80%9D%20in%20UP%20and%20in%20Gorakhpur%2C%20which%20is%20his%20permanent%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGorakhpur%20is%20also%20the%20constituency%20of%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20despite%20life%20terms%20awarded%20to%20Amarmani%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Madhumani%2C%20newspaper%20reports%20and%20sting%20operations%20in%202015-16%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20have%20been%20enjoying%20a%20luxurious%20life%20in%20a%20hospital%20at%20his%20home%20district%20where%20he%20occupied%20a%20full%20area%20of%20the%20government%20hospital%2C%20and%20in%20complete%20mockery%20of%20justice%2C%20they%20were%20undergoing%20life%20imprisonment%20just%20for%20namesake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20he%20was%20shifted%20back%20to%20jail%20from%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20jail%20authorities%20provided%20all%20facilities%20to%20them%2C%20including%20a%20mobile%20phone%20and%20a%20laptop.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20were%20provided%20with%20two%20barracks%20while%20usually%2C%20150%20to%20200%20common%20prisoners%2Fconvicts%20were%20kept%20in%20each%20barrack%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20said%20that%20while%20several%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20appeals%20filed%20by%20Nidhi%20Shukla%20about%20their%20time%20in%20hospitals%20and%20prison%20are%20still%20pending%2C%20according%20to%20one%20reply%20received%20in%202021%2C%20both%20Amarmani%20and%20Madhumani%20had%20spent%20about%20six%20years%20each%20in%20hospitals%20instead%20of%20being%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20thus%20stated%20that%20the%20couple%20made%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20court%20verdicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20Nidhi%20Shukla%2C%20after%20receiving%20%E2%80%9Cconstant%20threats%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Tripathis%E2%80%99%20son%20Amanmani%20Tripathi%2C%20made%20several%20representations%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20the%20principal%20secretary%2C%20Home%2C%20Lucknow%20for%20her%20and%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanmani%20Tripathi%20has%20also%20been%20a%20MLA%20after%20he%20won%20the%202017%20election%20from%20the%20Nautanwa%20constituency%20as%20an%20independent.%20He%20also%20contested%20the%202022%20election%2C%20but%20was%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamajwadi-s-aman-mani-tripathi-arrested-for-role-in-wife-s-murder%2Fstory-RaoiKhA9MkfwTPXp5Dr5NL.html%5C%22%3Earrested%20in%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20his%20wife%20Sara%2C%20who%20died%20in%20an%20alleged%20road%20accident%20in%202015.%20He%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-rejects-pleas-challenging-bail-granted-to-amanmani-tripathi%2Farticleshow%2F63819089.cms%5C%22%3Egranted%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%E2%80%99s%20petition%20said%20that%20it%20was%20being%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20her%20several%20representations%20%E2%80%9Cvehemently%20opposed%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20premature%20release%20of%20the%20Tripathis%20have%20gone%20%E2%80%9Cunanswered%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20has%20been%20misled%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EShukla%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20found%20merit%20in%20her%20documents%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20has%20been%20misled.%20All%20the%20authorities%20have%20all%20the%20documents.%20We%20have%20proof%20including%20RTI%20documents.%20We%20have%20filed%20all%20our%20papers%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20documents%2C%20the%20court%20accepted%20my%20plea%20and%20found%20truth%20in%20these%20papers%20but%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20and%20that%20is%20why%20this%20release%20was%20ordered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20while%20the%20release%20has%20been%20ordered%20citing%20old%20age%20and%20illness%2C%20it%20is%20widely%20known%20that%20the%20Tripathis%20are%20not%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20they%20are%20citing%20their%20old%20age%20and%20ill%20health%20%E2%80%93%20the%20whole%20country%20knows%20that%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20is%20not%20ill%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20she%20has%20no%20hopes%20for%20justice%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20not%20getting%20justice%20here%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20Uttarakhand.%20It%20is%20evident%20for%20years%20that%20justice%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20the%20Tripathis%20have%20been%20released%20because%20the%20remission%20plea%20came%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20then-SP%20government%20had%20said%20that%20since%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20Uttarakhand%2C%20they%20could%20not%20decide%20on%20it%20(remission%20plea).%20In%20Uttarakhand%20as%20well%2C%20the%20case%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20governor%20several%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20(UP)%20which%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20send%20him%20to%20jail%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20release%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20documents%20clearly%20say%20that%20he%20has%20been%20living%20at%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20doorstep%20in%20Gorakhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20saying%20this%2C%20the%20documents%20are%20saying%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20she%20has%20written%20several%20letters%20in%20the%20last%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%2012%20years%2C%20every%2015%20days%20I%20have%20written%20letters%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20wont%20get%20justice%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20that%20is%20when%20I%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20has%20since%20written%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20well%20as%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20why%20is%20the%20chief%20minister%20not%20even%20asking%20what%20documents%20are%20being%20spoken%20about%20(in%20the%20media)%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdubious-record-a-progress-report-on-ups-law-and-order-under-the-bjp-govt%5C%22%3EDubious%20Record%3A%20A%20Progress%20Report%20on%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Law%20and%20Order%20Under%20the%20BJP%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CYogi%20Adityanath%20is%20my%20guardian%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tripathi%E2%80%99s%20son%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanmani%20Tripathi%20said%20that%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20treatment%20followed%20all%20legal%20procedures.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20their%20release%20did%20not%20come%20through%20preferential%20treatment%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20no%20push%20from%20the%20state%20government.%20There%20is%20a%20law%20and%20I%20am%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20And%20I%20have%20the%20same%20rights%20as%20all%20other%20citizens.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20given%20its%20decision%20after%20we%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20however%2C%20that%20his%20family%20has%20had%20close%20ties%20with%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20an%20independent%20MLA%20in%202017%2C%20at%20the%20time%20Yogi%20ji%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Before%20that%20he%20was%20an%20MP%20from%20Gorakhpur.%20The%20distance%20between%20my%20residence%20and%20Gorakhnath%20temple%20(where%20Adityanath%20was%20the%20chief%20priest)%20is%20approximately%20500%20metres.%20We%20have%20very%20good%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20visiting%20the%20temple%20since%20he%20was%20a%20child%20and%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%20too%20have%20been%20going%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20parents%20were%20in%20jail%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20someone%20with%20whom%20I%20used%20to%20share%20personal%2C%20political%20and%20family%20problems.%20He%20used%20to%20give%20me%20advice%20like%20a%20guardian.%20And%20there%20are%20many%20such%20guardians%20from%20Gorakhpur%20Temple%20who%20used%20to%20give%20me%20advice.%20But%20yes%2C%20Yogi%20ji%20is%20my%20guardian%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20hospital%20in%20jail%20itself%20and%20if%20the%20jail%20hospital%20is%20not%20able%20to%20treat%20them%2C%20they%20will%20refer%20them%20to%20a%20higher%20centre%2C%20which%20is%20either%20a%20civil%20hospital%20or%20a%20district%20hospital.%20This%20is%20the%20law%20and%20this%20is%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20said%2C%20while%20refuting%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20person%20is%20in%20jail%20and%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%2C%20there%20is%20a%20specific%20organisation%20that%20looks%20into%20every%20aspect%20and%20decisions%20go%20through%20them%20and%20if%20they%20are%20found%20to%20be%20fine%2C%20they%20send%20them%20back%20to%20jail.%20No%20one%20can%20just%20go%20to%20a%20hospital%20and%20stay%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20their%20release%20order%2C%20his%20parents%20are%20seriously%20ill%20and%20continue%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20still%20in%20the%20hospital%20as%20they%20are%20seriously%20ill.%20My%20father%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20spinal%20neurological%20problem.%20If%20he%20walks%2C%20he%20falls%20down.%20My%20mother%20has%20severe%20psychiatric%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20release%20order%20has%20come%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdream%20come%20true%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20family%20and%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20like%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20Our%20family%2C%20supporters%20and%20well-wishers%20had%20the%20faith%20that%20one%20day%20we%20will%20win%20and%20when%20we%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20order%20of%20their%20release%2C%20we%20were%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanmani%20refuted%20allegations%20that%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20release%20had%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election%20in%202024%2C%20where%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20political%20influence%20could%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20thinking%20of%20politics%20as%20of%20now.%20We%2C%20as%20a%20family%2C%20are%20cherishing%20this%20moment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20he%20has%20been%20away%20from%20politics.%20He%20won%20his%20last%20election%20in%202007.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20contesting%20from%20his%20seat.%20Many%20elections%20have%20come%20and%20gone%20in%20between.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffive-years-of-incarceration-and-the-audacity-of-hope%5C%22%3EFive%20Years%20of%20Incarceration%20%E2%80%93%20And%20the%20Audacity%20of%20Hope%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20prisoners%20in%20jail%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20while%20Amanmani%20Tripathi%20can%20claim%20that%20he%20has%20old%20family%20ties%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20she%20is%20simply%20an%20ordinary%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20say%20that%20I%20have%20family%20relations%20with%20Yogi%20ji%20because%20I%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Like%20he%20is%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20the%20common%20people%2C%20he%20is%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20me%20as%20well.%20But%20Amanmani%20is%20saying%20proudly%20that%20he%20has%20familial%20ties%20with%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20her%20only%20demand%20now%20is%20that%20the%20Tripathis%E2%80%99%20release%20should%20be%20reversed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20only%20request%20those%20in%20power%2C%20to%20give%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20show%20our%20documents%20and%20act%20against%20those%20officers%20who%20have%20cleared%20their%20release.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20(Anandiben%20Patel)%20has%20special%20powers.%20She%20can%20peruse%20the%20two%20sets%20of%20documents%20%E2%80%93%20those%20given%20by%20the%20state%20government%20and%20those%20sent%20by%20me%2C%20and%20she%20can%20decide%20on%20her%20own%20on%20Amarmani%E2%80%99s%20release.%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20show%20the%20documents%20again%20and%20ready%20for%20a%20point%20by%20point%20debate%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20thousands%20of%20prisoners%20who%20are%20languishing%20in%20jails%20for%20years%20even%20at%2080%20years%20of%20age%20and%20have%20good%20behaviour.%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20being%20released%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693407245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25112256%2Fdownload-2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fim-scared-got-death-threats-slain-poets-sister-nidhi-shukla-after-former-up-ministers-release%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20UP%20minister%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20were%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence%2C%20were%20released%20on%20August%2024.%20Their%20son%2C%20Amanmani%2C%20said%20that%20while%20there%20was%20no%20push%20for%20his%20parents'%20release%20from%20the%20state%20government%2C%20CM%20Adityanath%20is%20his%20%E2%80%98guardian%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fim-scared-got-death-threats-slain-poets-sister-nidhi-shukla-after-former-up-ministers-release%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20key%20areas%20where%20drones%20have%20allowed%20Ukraine%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20over%20Russia%20%7C%20Sean%20Bell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693406520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-drone-strike-russian-warplane_6268126.jpg%3F20230830173240%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fukraine-war-three-key-areas-where-drones-have-allowed-zelenskyys-forces-to-take-the-initiative-over-russia-12950892%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alt