2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125649%2FIMG_4764.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20article%20in%20a%20four-part%20reportage%20series%20from%20Kishtwar%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20You%20can%20read%20the%20first%20and%20second%20articles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fjk-will-the-renewed-hunt-for-sapphires-aid-the-devlopment-of-neglected-kishtwar%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-projects-in-kishtwar-light-up-homes-in-other-states-but-not-this-hamlet-in-the-region%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20final%20article%20will%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrabshalla%20(Kishtwar)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Every%20day%2C%20when%20Mohammad%20Abban%20(8)%20returns%20from%20school%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20Nazia%20Akhtar%2C%20a%20housewife%2C%20confines%20him%20to%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20their%20double-storied%20home%20in%20Drabshalla%20town%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kishtwar%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20walking%20distance%20from%20their%20house%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20playgrounds%20in%20this%20mountainous%20village%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20potential%20killing%20field%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Ratle%20power%20project%20which%20has%20picked%20pace%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20say%20they%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20explosions%2C%20which%20often%20take%20place%20allegedly%20without%20warning%2C%20and%20shards%20of%20stones%20rain%20down%20on%20their%20rooftops%2C%20scaring%20the%20villagers%20out%20of%20their%20wits%2C%20especially%20children%20and%20the%20elderly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMother%20tells%20me%20that%20it%20is%20not%20safe%20to%20go%20out%2C%20so%20I%20play%20inside%20the%20home.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20as%20good%20as%20playing%20with%20friends%20in%20the%20ground.%20There%20is%20no%20fun%20and%20excitement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abban%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20construction%20workers%20guided%20by%20engineers%20who%20are%20armed%20with%20hi-tech%20gadgets%2C%20mountain-cutting%20machinery%2C%20and%20heavy%20load%20carriers%20are%20fighting%20deadlines%20and%20climate%20change%20to%20finish%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20run-of-the-river%20Ratle%20hydropower%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESet%20to%20be%20commissioned%20in%202026%2C%20the%20Rs%203%2C300%20crore%20project%20is%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20in%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20a%20majority%20stakeholder.%20Over%20427%20hectares%20of%20land%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20for%20the%20project%20of%20which%20373%20is%20forest%20land%2C%20including%2075%20hectare%20river%20bed%2C%20while%2016%20hectares%20is%20private%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125458%2FIMG_4747.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125458%2FIMG_4747.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125458%2FIMG_4747-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125458%2FIMG_4747-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EConstruction%20activity%20is%20in%20full%20swing%20at%20Drabshalla%20for%20building%20the%20Ratle%20power%20plant.%20Access%20roads%20have%20already%20been%20completed%20and%20tunnels%20are%20being%20constructed.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prestigious%20project%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20several%20hydropower%20projects%20coming%20up%20on%20the%20Chenab%20river%2C%20is%20located%20in%20Seismic%20Zone%20IV%20of%20the%20central%20crystalline%20belt%20in%20the%20Great%20Himalayas%2C%20which%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintense%20tectonic%20deformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20an%20official%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202012%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%20shows%20that%20the%20project%20was%20going%20to%20affect%2046%20families%20comprising%20285%20persons%20in%20Kandini%20village%2C%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20submergence%20zone%2C%20and%2016%20families%20comprising%20over%20100%20persons%20in%20Drabshalla%2C%20which%20will%20host%20the%20dam%20and%20the%20power%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgovernment%2Fkashmir-new-ratle-hydroelectric-power-projects-economically-viable%2F%5C%22%3EAre%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20New%20Hydro-Electric%20Projects%20Economically%20Viable%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20Omar%20Abdullah%20government%20in%202012%2C%20missed%20multiple%20deadlines%20due%20to%20poor%20execution%20and%20lack%20of%20finances%2C%20spiking%20the%20number%20of%20project-affected%20persons%20(PAFs)%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20gave%20a%20fresh%20go-ahead%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20upstream%20of%20the%20450MW%20Baghlihar%20project%20and%20downstream%20of%20the%20390MW%20Dulhasti%20project%20in%20Kishtwar%2C%20the%20Ratle%20project%20envisions%20the%20construction%20of%20two%2C%2011-metre%20circular%20diversion%20tunnels%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20completed%20last%20year%2C%20and%20four%2C%206.6%20metre%20pressure%20shaft%20tunnels%2C%20along%20with%20a%20133-metre%20concrete%20dam%2C%20reservoir%2C%20underground%20powerhouse%2C%20and%20access%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20850%20MW%20project%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%203%2C136%20million%20units%20of%20electricity%20a%20year%2C%2084%25%20of%20which%20will%20be%20sold%20as%20merchant%20power%20while%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20get%20only%2016%25%20free%20power%2C%20as%20per%20the%20agreement%20signed%20by%20the%20GoI-owned%20National%20Hydel%20Power%20Company%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20State%20Power%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Indus%20Water%20Treaty%2C%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20a%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20are%20adjudicating%20the%20dispute%20over%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20power%20project%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Chenab%20Valley%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fbusiness%2Fpakistan-objects-to-indias-work-on-hydro-power-project%5C%22%3EPakistan%20raised%20objections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20which%20is%20being%20steamrolled%20by%20the%20government%20even%20as%20the%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation%20Programme%20for%20the%20affected%20households%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20approved%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20by%20the%20contractor.%20A%20video%20captured%20by%20locals%20recently%20showed%20heavy%20trucks%20dumping%20the%20material%20excavated%20from%20the%20project%20site%20into%20the%20Chenab%20river%2C%20in%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20destroy%20the%20river%20ecosystem%20and%20change%20the%20flow%20(of%20the%20river)%2C%E2%80%9D%20G.M.%20Bhat%2C%20a%20senior%20geologist%20who%20has%20extensively%20studied%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hyderabad-based%20company%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructure%20Limited%2C%20which%20is%20executing%20the%20project%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20under-construction%20tunnels%20of%20the%20project%20was%20damaged%20in%20a%20recent%20flood%20triggered%20by%20heavy%20rains%20across%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%2C%20which%20could%20delay%20the%20commissioning%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20small%20community%20living%20atop%20a%20hill%20flanked%20by%20the%20Chenab%20river%2C%20where%20the%20construction%20work%20is%20underway%2C%20have%20been%20left%20out%20of%20the%20rehabilitation%20programme.%20The%20community%20is%20separated%20from%20the%20main%20Drabshalla%20town%20by%20the%20Doda-Kishtwar%20highway%20and%20the%20construction%20activity%20has%20spawned%20endless%20miseries%20and%20a%20pervasive%20fear%20of%20destruction%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30133203%2FIMG_4775.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30133203%2FIMG_4775.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30133203%2FIMG_4775-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30133203%2FIMG_4775-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20group%20of%20workers%20employed%20at%20the%20Ratle%20power%20project%20stand%20in%20a%20queue%20outside%20an%20ATM%20in%20Drabshalla%20town%20of%20Kishtwar.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20heavy%20explosives%20are%20being%20used%20to%20dig%20tunnels%20for%20the%20power%20project%2C%20several%20houses%20in%20Drabshalla%20have%20developed%20cracks%2C%20making%20them%20unsafe.%20Due%20to%20heavy%20blasting%2C%20shards%20of%20stones%20are%20propelled%20into%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChenab%20Valley%20sits%20in%20the%20seismically%20active%20Himalayan%20region.%20Kishtwar%20district%20is%20located%20in%20a%20region%20of%20high-risk%20seismic%20activity%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20tremors%20originating%20from%20Chenab%20Valley%20this%20year%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20region%20has%20not%20witnessed%20any%20major%20seismic%20activity%20%E2%80%93%20the%20last%20major%20earthquake%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20reported%20in%202005%20%E2%80%93%20the%20blasting%20activity%20increases%20the%20chances%20of%20rockslides%20and%20decreases%20the%20mountain%E2%80%99s%20stability%2C%20making%20the%20village%20prone%20to%20more%20natural%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20four%20people%20died%20and%20six%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20landslide%20struck%20the%20power%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20locals%2C%20the%20earth%20shakes%20and%20stones%20rain%20down%20on%20their%20houses%20when%20explosions%20are%20carried%20out%2C%20giving%20them%20restless%20days%20and%20sleepless%20nights.%20While%20the%20playground%20remains%20largely%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20the%20children%2C%20the%20streets%20wear%20deserted%20looks%20and%20the%20shops%20are%20covered%20under%20a%20layer%20of%20dust%20blown%20into%20the%20air%20by%20the%20blasting%20and%20other%20construction%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20pollution%20caused%20by%20dust%20which%20will%20be%20addressed%20very%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Kishtwar%20Devansh%20Yadav%2C%20admitted%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20denying%20that%20the%20construction%20activity%20was%20impacting%20the%20residential%20houses%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DC%20said%20that%20the%20project%20has%20generated%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20locals%2C%20%E2%80%9C230%20persons%20out%20of%20250%2C%20whose%20land%20was%20acquired%20for%20building%20the%20project%2C%20have%20been%20provided%20employment%20and%20more%20jobs%20are%20going%20to%20open%20as%20the%20construction%20gathers%20steam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20local%20residents%2C%20whose%20houses%20have%20developed%20cracks%20allegedly%20due%20to%20the%20explosions%2C%20blame%20the%20administration%20for%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20most%20days%2C%20we%20wake%20up%20in%20terror%20due%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20blasts.%20In%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20the%20blasting%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20evenings.%20A%20siren%20used%20to%20blow%20before%20the%20explosions.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20schedule%20or%20warning%20now.%20It%20can%20happen%20at%20anytime%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jyoti%20Parihar%2C%20mother%20of%20two%20minor%20children%20aged%20eight%20and%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20there%20are%20explosions%20during%20the%20daytime%20also.%20Stones%20fly%20in%20the%20air%20and%20some%20of%20them%20rain%20down%20on%20our%20homes%20too.%20I%20had%20a%20narrow%20escape%20myself%20recently%2C%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20Nazia%20Akhtar%2C%20Abban%E2%80%99s%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DC%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20has%20installed%20seismometers%20in%20Drabshalla%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20%E2%80%9Cto%20ensure%20that%20the%20blasting%20activity%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exceed%20the%20threshold%E2%80%9D%20which%20causes%20damage%20to%20concrete%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CResidents%20might%20have%20some%20grievances%20but%20the%20administration%20is%20committed%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20taken%20care%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20local%20residents%20are%20not%20content%20with%20official%20assurances.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mechanism%20of%20seismometers%20will%20protect%20only%20concrete%20buildings.%20What%20about%20those%20buildings%20which%20are%20not%20made%20of%20concrete%3F%20My%20house%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20collapsing%20but%20instead%20of%20listening%20to%20our%20genuine%20grievances%2C%20we%20are%20being%20threatened%20with%20police%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdul%20Haq%20Mattoo%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Drabshalla%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693405832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30125649%2FIMG_4764.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-blasting-ratle-power-project-seisimic-zone%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20houses%20in%20Drabshalla%20have%20developed%20cracks%2C%20making%20them%20unsafe.%20Locals%20say%20the%20earth%20shakes%20and%20stones%20rain%20down%20on%20their%20houses%2C%20giving%20them%20sleepless%20nights.%20The%20project%2C%20which%20is%20coming%20up%20on%20Chenab%20River%2C%20is%20located%20in%20a%20seismic%20zone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-blasting-ratle-power-project-seisimic-zone%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20B-Town%20celebrated%20Raksha%20Bandhan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693405800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103217842%2Cimgsize-146814.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsara-ali-khan-taimur-jeh-varun-dhawan-sanjay-dutt-raksha-bandhan-2023-photos-of-b-town-celebs%2Fphotostory%2F103217842.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103217842.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BSara%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20Taimur%2C%20Jeh%2C%20Varun%20Dhawan%2C%20Sanjay%20Dutt%3A%