rong%2Farticleshow%2F103217892.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22California%20Legislature%20Passes%20Historic%20Anti-Caste%20Discrimination%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30180818%2FSB-403-1200.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20California%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20has%20passed%20Senate%20Bill%20(SB)%20403%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20add%20caste%20among%20the%20categories%20officially%20protected%20from%20discrimination%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20Assembly%2C%20the%20state%20legislature%E2%80%99s%20lower%20house%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsacbee.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-government%2Fcapitol-alert%2Farticle278708489.html%5C%22%3Epassed%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%2055-3%20majority%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20(August%2028).%20The%20Senate%20(the%20upper%20house)%20had%20passed%20it%20by%20a%2034-1%20majority%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20rights%20activist%20Thenmozhi%20Soundararajan%2C%20who%20is%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20celebrated%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20passage%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwin%20for%20the%20ages%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assembly%20vote%20is%20a%20win%20for%20the%20ages.%20After%20conducting%20over%20700%20advocacy%20meetings%20across%20the%20entire%20state%20of%20California%2C%20the%20people%20have%20spoken%20resoundingly%20for%20caste%20equity%20protections.%20As%20a%20Californian%20who%20has%20endured%20caste%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20I%20know%20the%20struggles%20and%20adversity%20caste-oppressed%20Californians%20have%20unjustly%20faced%20first-hand%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Associated%20Press%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthehindu.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fcalifornia-assembly-passes-anti-caste-discrimination-bill%2Farticle67247356.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%20her%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoundararajan%20is%20a%20founder%20of%20Equality%20Labs%2C%20an%20Ambedkarite%20organisation%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-65819688%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20forefront%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%20supporting%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambedkar%20Association%20of%20North%20America%20(AANA)%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20vote%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20remembered%20for%20generations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCaste%20discrimination%2C%20a%20deeply%20entrenched%20issue%20impacting%20countless%20lives%2C%20finds%20itself%20squarely%20addressed%20in%20SB%20403.%20The%20Bill%20introduces%20comprehensive%20measures%20to%20counter%20discrimination%20across%20sectors%20such%20as%20education%2C%20employment%2C%20housing%20and%20public%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESupporters%20come%20out%20to%20celebrate.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqmIcDKbYw9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqmIcDKbYw9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Sameea%20Kamal%20(%40SameeaKamal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSameeaKamal%2Fstatus%2F1696295882088501510%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawmaker%20Aisha%20Wahab%2C%20who%20introduced%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20California%20Senate%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20thanked%20members%20of%20the%20Assembly%20for%20voting%20in%20favour%20of%20SB%20403%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESacramento%20Bee%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20is%20happy%20about%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20diaspora%20groups%20have%20opposed%20SB%20403%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2F