0the%20fear%20of%20exposing%20intelligence%20agents%20and%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20known%20how%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idi.org.il%2Farticles%2F28782%5C%22%3Ehundreds%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20belong%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20most%20of%20the%20Israeli%20far%20right%20terrorist%20incidents%20in%20the%20West%20Ban%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Elisha%20Yered%20is%20identified%20with%20them%20%E2%80%93%20are%20agents%20or%20collaborators%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20in%20retrospect%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenation.com%2Farticle%2Fsociety%2Fhoover-fbi-gman-gospel%2F%5C%22%3Eduring%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20years%20of%20political%20persecution%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20head%20of%20the%20FBI%20J.%20Edgar%20Hoover%2C%20out%20of%20about%205%2C000%20members%20of%20the%20American%20Communist%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20about%201%2C500%20were%20agents%20and%20collaborators%20of%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover-300x214.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover-1024x731.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJ.%20Edgar%20Hoover.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FFBI%2C%20Public%20Domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C