journalist%20Elisha%20Ben-Kimon%20on%20February%204%2C%202022%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vehicle%20used%20in%20the%20chain%20of%20incidents%20in%20Mahmada%E2%80%99s%20plant%20nursery%20belonged%20to%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%20A%20Shin%20Bet%20agent%20who%20was%20implanted%20in%20the%20cell%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20participated%20in%20the%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20complaint%20submitted%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20state%20prosecutor%20for%20special%20duties%20against%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20on%20June%202022%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Crecently%20a%20response%20was%20received%20from%20some%20of%20the%20parties%20to%20whom%20the%20complaint%20was%20forwarded.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20content%20of%20the%20response%20received%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20deepen%20the%20investigation%20and%20forward%20your%20request%20to%20additional%20parties%20in%20order%20to%20exhaust%20the%20investigation.%20Another%20update%20will%20be%20sent%20after%20all%20the%20responses%20have%20been%20examined%20and%20when%20a%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20on%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Mahmada%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20decision%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20Israel%20Police%20continued%20to%20act%20negligently%2C%20did%20not%20recognise%20the%20incidents%20as%20terrorist%20incidents%2C%20and%20the%20deputy%20state%20prosecutor%20for%20special%20duties%20continued%20to%20drag%20his%20feet%20in%20investigating%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%20Therefore%2C%20perhaps%20it%20is%20no%20wonder%20that%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2019%2C%202022%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kan.org.il%2Fcontent%2Fkan-news%2Fdefense%2F245069%2F%5C%22%3Esixth%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20place%20at%20Mahmada%E2%80%99s%20plant%20nursery%2C%20which%20was%20a%20step%20up%20in%20violence.%20The%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20cell%20arrived%20again%2C%20made%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20wall