r%20ways%2C%20but%20refrains%20from%20stopping%20such%20activity%20in%20real-time%20or%20sharing%20evidence%20with%20the%20police%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20be%20prosecuted%20%E2%80%93%20except%20in%20exceptional%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20way%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20is%20taken%20for%20questioning%2C%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20investigators%20can%20lay%20out%20before%20him%20all%20the%20terrorist%20incidents%20that%20they%20know%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20%E2%80%9Csurprised%E2%80%9D%20suspect%20can%20%E2%80%9Cchoose%E2%80%9D%20whether%20to%20admit%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20specific%20incident%20for%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%20or%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20the%20multitude%20of%20terror%20incidents%20that%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20knows%20about%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sometimes%20to%20consider%20whether%20to%20become%20a%20collaborator%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20emerges%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nevo.co.il%2Fpsika_html%2Fmechozi%2FME-16-01-932-22.htm%5C%22%3Efacts%20of%20the%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20against%20Amiram%20Ben%20Uliel%20who%20was%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20the%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2022-09-01%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisrael-supreme-court-rejects-appeal-of-israeli-who-murdered-palestinian-family-in-2015%2F00000182-f785-d67e-a5a3-f7cd11c60000%5C%22%3EDawabsha%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20setting%20on%20fire%20their%20home%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20town%20of%20Duma%2C%20south%20of%20Nablus%2C%20while%20they%20were%20sleeping.%20There%20it%20is%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20known%20to%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20and%20operated%20for%20two%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20incident%20as%20part%20of%20a%20new%20terror%20cell%20of%20far-right%20activists%20who%20sought%20to%20promote%20an%20extreme%20and%20violent%20ideological%20concept%20aimed%20at%20destabilising%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20through%20the%20use%20of%20terrorism%20and%20violence%2C%20including%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20is%20implied%20in%20the%20indictment%20filed%20against%20Ben%20Uliel%20that%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20did%20not%20stop%20his%20terror%20cell%20in%20real%20time.%20At%20a%20closed%20conference%20of%20the%20Likud%20Party%E2%80%99s%20youth%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20the%20then%20minister%20of%20defence%20Moshe%20%E2%80%9CBogie%E2%80%9D%20Ya%E2%80%99alon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Farticles%2F0%2C7340%2CL-4699818%2C00.html%5C%22%3Eadmitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20security%20services%20knew%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Dawabsha%20family%E2%80%99s%20home%20but%20avoided%20prosecuting%20him%20so%20as%20not%20to%20reveal%20intelligence%20sources%20in%20the%20court.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20tremendous%20public%20and%20political%20pressure%20exerted%20on%20Israel%20following%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20parents%20and%20their%20one-and-a-half-year-old%20son%2C%20an%20indictment%20was%20filed%20against%20Ben%20Uliel%20and%20another%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20this%20modus%20operandi%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20reduce%20Israeli%20far-right%20terrorism%20or%20encourage%20it%20and%20give%20such%20activists%20a%20free%20hand%3F%20Since%20there%20is%20no%20transparency%20regarding%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20make%20an%20overall%20objective%20assessment.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20who%20is%20paying%20the%20price.%20This%20is%20an%20experiment%20on%20Palestinian%20human%20beings%20who%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20are%20not%20recognised%20by%20most%20of%20the%20Israeli%20media%20and%20public%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20experiment%20on%20them%20can%20continue%20without%20interruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAttorney%20Eitay%20Mack%20represents%2