2%3Cp%3EDr%20Pramila%20Sanjaya%20has%20lived%20in%20Jaipur%20for%20over%2060%20years.%20Through%20this%20time%2C%20she%20has%20watched%20the%20city%20grow%20and%20expand%20over%20existing%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20used%20to%20be%20farms%20have%20now%20been%20converted%20into%20colonies%20and%20taken%20over%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291949%2Fmumbai-urban-gardener-grows-passion-fruits-and-beekeeps-on-terrace-garden-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistory%20buildings%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20have%20also%20witnessed%20is%20the%20growth%20of%20informal%20settlements%20and%20slums%20across%20the%20city%2C%20which%20did%20not%20exist%20during%20my%20childhood.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrateek%20Tiwari%2C%20another%20Jaipur%20resident%20and%20CEO%20of%C2%A0%20Living%20Greens%20Organics%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20also%20recalls%20a%20time%20when%20the%20city%20centre%20was%20full%20of%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%E2%80%99d%20visit%20my%20grandparents%20in%20Jaipur%20during%20May%2C%20summers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20something%20we%20would%20dread.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20stay%20indoors%20between%2011%20am%20and%203%20pm%20%E2%80%94%20when%20it%20was%20very%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20but%20by%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20temperature%20would%20drop%20and%20it%20would%20be%20pleasantly%20cool%2C%20enough%20for%20us%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20terrace%20at%20night.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20no%20longer%20have%20those%20spaces%20that%20helped%20keep%20the%20city%20cool.%20Jaipur%20has%20changed%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20is%20only%20one%20among%20the%20several%20Indian%20cities%20facing%20rising%20incidents%20of%20extreme%20heat%20and%20water%20scarcity.%20Meanwhile%2C%20coastal%20cities%20like%20Kochi%20and%20Mumbai%20are