acilities-in-aksai-chin-to-protect-military-assets-101693323895447.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20analysing%20satellite%20imagery%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constructions%20are%20at%20a%20location%20about%2070km%20from%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20or%20LAC%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20had%20reported%20after%20studying%20satellite%20imagery%20in%20May%20that%20China%20had%20built%20new%20runways%2C%20ramped%20up%20jet%20protection%20shelters%20and%20built%20new%20buildings%20for%20support%20and%20military%20operations.%20All%20this%20was%20to%20expand%20its%20airbases%20along%20the%20LAC%20and%20to%20allow%20it%20to%20conduct%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwider%20range%20of%20operations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%20China%20also%20sought%20to%20counter%20India%E2%80%99s%20relative%20advantage%20in%20some%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20outlet%20reports%20that%20the%20personnel%20bunkers%20have%20been%20reinforced.%20What%20gives%20this%20away%20is%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Chave%20earth%20raised%20around%20them%20to%20provide%20additional%20protection%20from%20aerial%20or%20missile%20attacks%E2%80%9D.%20In%20addition%2C%20entry%20and%20exit%20points%20are%20designed%20in%20a%20forked%20manner%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20dissipate%20the%20impact%20of%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20carries%C2%A0%20photographs%20from%20as%20recently%20as%20August%2018%2C%20showing%20what%20the%20outlet%20identifies%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20development%20of%20underground%20facilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20says%20that%20a%20comparison%20of%20images%20taken%20on%20December%206%2C%202021%2C%20and%20August%2018%20this%20year%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20Chinese%20have%20built%20ramped%20up%20bunkers%20and%20done%20underground%20construction%20at%20six%20locations%2C%20within%2015%20square%20kilometres%20of%20Aksai%20Chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20notes%20new%20development%20activity%20in%20the%20same%20region%2C%20including%20new%20roads%2C%20tunnels%2C%20new%20entrances%20and%20bunkers%20for%20soldiers.%20Hillsides%20in%20some%20places%20are%20being%20dug%20up%20for%20new%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20officials%20have%20not%20commented%20on%20this%20analysis%20by%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fnew-china-map-continues-to-show-whole-of-arunachal-pradesh-as-part-of-china%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20China%20government%E2%80%99s%202023%20edition%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20standard%20map%2C%20released%20on%20August%2028%2C%20continues%20to%20show%20the%20whole%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20region%20as%20part%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20stated%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20protest%E2%80%9D%20was%20lodged%20with%20the%20Chinese%20that%20such%20moves%20%E2%80%9Ccomplicate%E2%80%9D%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20larger%20boundary%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693397676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30174145%2FScreenshot-2023-08-30-at-5.41.07.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchina-india-lac-aksai-chin-construction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Hindustan%20Times'%20reports%20that%20a%20comparison%20of%20images%20taken%20on%20December%206%2C%202021%2C%20and%20August%2018%20this%20year%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20Chinese%20have%20built%20ramped%20up%20bunkers%20and%20done%20underground%20construction%20at%20six%20locations%2C%20within%2015%20square%20kilometres%20of%20Aksai%20Chin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchina-india-lac-aksai-chin-construction%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Stock%20Is%20Falling%20and%20It%20Shows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27140126%2FNarendra-Modi-in-Manipur.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20establishment%20has%20a%20problem.%20Its%20stock%20is%20falling.%20There%20is%20another%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20wrangling%20at%20the%20top%20which%20is%20becoming%20visible.%20The%20negativity%20can%20get%20even%20more%20serious%20if%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20ideological%20and%20political%20opponents%20are%20able%20to%20bring%20greater%20cohesion%20and%20clarity%20to%20their%20stated%20goal%20of%20dethroning%20the%20regime%20in%20the%20next%20parliamentary%20election%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20held%20early%20next%20year%20as%20scheduled%2C%20or%20along%20with%20a%20clutch%20of%20key%20state%20polls%20later%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheduled%20Mumbai%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20(August%2031-September%201)%20should%20be%20a%20pointer%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20expected%20mutual%20cooperation%20among%20the%20partners%20and%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20practical%20steps%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20opponents%20can%20credibly%20muster.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20atmospherics%20are%2C%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20positive%20though%20these%20could%20have%20been%20better.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20basic%20question%20too%3A%20Can%20all%20the%20parties%20of%20the%20conglomerate-in-the-making%20resist%20the%20high-scale%20coercion%20the%20establishment%20can%20bring%20on%2C%20and%20stick%20it%20out%20to%20the%20end%3F%20Maharashtra%20affairs%20are%20worth%20watching%20in%20this%20context%2C%20but%20also%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20can%20some%20regional%20leaders%20resist%20personal%20ambitions%20and%20not%20fight%20two%20battles%20simultaneously%20%E2%80%93%20one%20to%20defeat%20the%20quasi-dictatorship%2C%20and%20two%20to%20promote%20their%20personal%20or%20party%20interests%3F%20They%20probably%20can%2C%20though%20it%20is%20best%20to%20be%20doubly%20sure.%20But%20if%20they%20fluff%20this%20one%2C%20they%20sink%20together.%20Swimming%20separately%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question.%20The%20regime%20would%20ensure%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20prominent%20opposition%20leaders%20now%20in%20the%20INDIA%20formation%20were%20advancing%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20context%2C%20the%20jaded%20and%20bizarre%20formula%20of%20striking%20out%20on%20an%20anti-BJP%2C%20anti-Congress%20path%2C%20self-servingly%20asserting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20difference%20between%20these%20parties.%20Such%20nonsense%20had%20no%20takers%20among%20the%20people%20and%20everyone%20made%20fun%20of%20the%20stunt%20growing%20out%20of%20the%20south%20and%20the%20east.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-has-discovered-that-modi-is-jaded-and-faded%5C%22%3EThe%20Opposition%20Has%20Discovered%20That%20Modi%20Is%20Jaded%20and%20Faded%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20once%20INDIA%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-opposition-parties-meet-in-bengaluru-here-are-the-9-big-factors-at-play%5C%22%3Eborn%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20an%20immaculate%20conception%20in%20Patna%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20playing%20a%20centripetal%20hand%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20began%20to%20fulminate%2C%20and%20then%20wilt.%20The%20wilting%20was%20on%20pathetic%20display%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20in%20parliament%20and%20his%20ritualistic%20address%20from%20Red%20Fort%20on%20Independence%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20popular%20perception%2C%20there%20was%20now%20at%20last%20the%20plausibility%20of%20resistance.%20The%20opposition%20parties%2C%20if%20they%20held%20fast%2C%20could%20challenge%20a%20regime%20that%20had%20become%20openly%20defiant%20of%20public%20opinion%2C%20openly%20oppressive%2C%20unrepentantly%20given%20to%20inflicting%20violence%20upon%20the%20people%2C%20and%20wantonly%20suppressing%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20in%20order%20to%20exalt%20the%20richest%20of%20the%20rich%20classes%2C%20and%20to%20jail%20those%20who%20dissented%20and%20protested.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20the%20moment%20when%20Modi%20slipped%20from%20the%20pedestal.%20The%20parallelogram%20of%20forces%20began%20to%20change%20direction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20change%20is%20still%20on%20the%20path%20to%20full%20realisation%20and%20will%20probably%20find%20its%20crystallised%20form%20after%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20confabulation.%20Nevertheless%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20the%20present%20conjuncture%20beckoned%20the%20rampaging%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20declare%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20recent%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20that%2C%20exactly%20like%20the%20demon-king%20Ravana%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20too%20heeds%20the%20advice%20of%20just%20two%20people%20%E2%80%93%20his%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20reality%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20just%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20voice%20counts.%20The%20indications%20are%20that%20Adani%20and%20Modi%20are%20peas%20in%20a%20pod.%20Reportedly%2C%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20doled%20out%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-govt-paid-rs-3-900-cr-of-excess-payment-to-adani-power-gohil-123082600845_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earound%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20an%20Adani%20enterprise%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithout%20bills%20being%20presented.%20Coincidence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20Gujarat%20Congress%20president%20Shaktisinh%20Gohil%20has%20reportedly%20produced%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Gujarat%20Urja%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Ltd%20to%20Adani%20Power%2C%20Mundra%2C%20in%20which%20the%20state%20power%20utility%20says%20it%20made%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexcess%20payment%E2%80%9D%20of%20Rs%203%2C900%20crore%20to%20Adani%20Power%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20This%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20Is%20this%20an%20example%20of%20poor%20accounting%20by%20a%20government%20enterprise%2C%20or%20political%20largesse%20%E2%80%93%20in%20effect%2C%20the%20Modi%20effect%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F669744%2Fadanis-acquisitions-india-needs-to-keep-track-costs%2F%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20Why%20India%20Needs%20to%20Keep%20Track%20of%20the%20Costs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20Shah%2C%20he%20is%20doubtless%2C%20clever%2C%20devious%2C%20energetic%20and%20a%20long-time%20lieutenant%20of%20Modi.%20But%20in%20the%20larger%20suspiciously%20turbulent%20intra-BJP%20dynamic%2C%20the%20question%20of%20where%20he%20stands%20will%20be%20asked.Forget%20the%20surface%20play%20%E2%80%93%20remember%2C%20the%20BJP-Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20are%20a%20semi-secret%20show.%20There%20is%20an%20illusion%20and%20there%20is%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20pin-pointed%20speech%20stands%20out%2C%20nevertheless.%20No%20opponent%20of%20Modi%20had%20before%20summoned%20the%20nerve%20to%20compare%20him%20with%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20arrogant%20adversary%2C%20the%20evil-doer%20of%20Hindu%20mythology%20who%20had%20dared%20to%20abduct%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20consort%2C%20Sita.%20Given%20this%2C%20Gandhi%20at%20once%20rose%20a%20few%20inches%20in%20public%20esteem%20when%20he%20voiced%20the%20thoughts%20of%20countless%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20tide%20was%20with%20him%20as%20he%20politically%20sought%20to%20indict%20the%20leader%20of%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%20he%20also%20cracked%20a%20state%20secret%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20head%20of%20government%20was%20putty%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20most%20notable%20representative%20of%20big%20business%20who%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20an%20international%20controversy%20over%20massive%20financial%20malpractices%2C%20although%20he%20denies%20this.%20It%20is%20becoming%20self-evident%20from%20the%20overall%20context%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20big%20pitch%20for%20Hindu%20voters%20%E2%80%93%20building%20a%20temple%20to%20Sri%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%93%20springs%20less%20from%20piety%20and%20more%20from%20the%20pursuit%20of%20power.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20noteworthy%20in%20the%20context%20of%20current%20political%20play%20is%20that%20no%20one%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%20rose%20to%20challenge%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20scathing%20assertions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20A%20late%20retort%20came%20from%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20who%20remained%20unmoved%20when%20a%20rape%20video%20surfaced%20from%20Manipur.%20As%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20leaving%20the%20House%2C%20in%20a%20revenge%20attack%2C%20she%20accused%20him%20of%20blowing%20a%20flying%20kiss%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20women%20on%20the%20treasury%20benches%20and%20complained%20to%20the%20Speaker!%20In%20effect%2C%20Modi%20was%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20himself%20by%20his%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20attacked%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20in%20season%20and%20out%20of%20season%2C%20in%20Parliament%20and%20outside.%20Distinctly%20feeling%20cornered%20when%20addressing%20the%20nation%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20Independence%20Day%2C%20he%20literally%20begged%20the%20people%20for%20%E2%80%9Chelp%E2%80%9D%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20single%20party%20(rather%20than%20an%20alliance).%20No%20other%20prime%20minister%20has%20used%20the%20Red%20Fort%20gathering%20on%20August%2015%20as%20an%20election%20rally%20before%2C%20but%20Modi%20is%20not%20above%20setting%20a%20dubious%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20birth%20of%20INDIA%2C%20the%20very%20notion%20of%20an%20opposition%20to%20Modi%20was%20reassuringly%20entertaining%20at%20best.%20With%20INDIA%20coming%20into%20play%2C%20everything%20began%20to%20look%20probable.%20The%20emergence%20of%20an%20opposition-for-itself%2C%20in%20short%20an%20opposition%20for%20the%20people%20in%20their%20dire%20hour%2C%20has%20now%20developed%20recognisable%20contours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gramsci%E2%80%99s%20famous%20postulation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20of%20position%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20ideological%20battlefield%20against%20the%20forces%20of%20fascism%2C%20it%20can%20now%20be%20posited%20that%20the%20emerging%20opposition%20bloc%20appears%20to%20have%20forged%20ahead%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20sycophantic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhakt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(BJP-RSS%20supporters)%20battalions%2C%20though%20the%20latter%20are%20never%20going%20to%20be%20short%20on%20fire%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20crunch%20situation%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20bhakts%20can%20unleash%20all%20kinds%20of%20resources%2C%20including%20high-octane%20propaganda.%20It%20can%20unleash%20the%20Election%20Commission%20itself%20by%20obliging%20it%20to%20resile%20from%20its%20constitutional%20stance%20of%20democratic%20neutrality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20now%20it%20is%20INDIA%2C%20especially%20its%20Congress%20component%2C%20which%20is%20setting%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20narratives%20and%20agenda.%20The%20so-called%20opinion%20polls%20run%20by%20television%20stations%20and%20others%2C%20and%20their%20laughable%20efforts%20of%20daring%20to%20tell%20India%20about%20her%20own%20political%20mood%20many%20months%20before%20an%20election%2C%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20massive%20exercise%20in%20deception%20%E2%80%93%20a%20command%20performance%20aimed%20at%20snatching%20away%20the%20initiative%20from%20the%20national%20opposition.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20it%20is%20doubtful%20if%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20play%20up%20a%20point%20of%20national%20glory%2C%20namely%20the%20superb%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20or%20the%20upcoming%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20can%20be%20notched%20up%20in%20the%20credit%20column%20for%20the%20prime%20minister.%20People%20are%20learning%20to%20watch%20critically.%20They%20would%20instinctively%20know%20that%20what%20is%20practically%20a%20ban%20on%20entering%20Delhi%20and%20on%20free%20movement%20within%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20is%20a%20police%20tactic%20to%20head%20off%20any%20possible%20protest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-g20-summit-closing-down-a-city%5C%22%3EClosing%20Down%20A%20City%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20autocracy%20is%20a%20one-trick%20pony.%20It%20can%20hope%20to%20rally%20its%20forces%20only%20within%20sections%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20community%20in%20hopes%20of%20maintaining%20hegemony%20on%20a%20communal%20basis%2C%20not%20democratically.%20This%20is%20achieved%20through%20the%20calibrated%20use%20of%20communal%20violence.%20We%20have%20seen%20this%20happen%20with%20focused%20intent%20since%20important%20state%20polls%20and%20the%20national%20elections%20are%20near.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlas%2C%20this%20is%20what%20India%20has%20been%20reduced%20to.%20The%20technique%20has%20been%20on%20display%20for%20more%20than%20three%20months%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20violence%20continues%20to%20be%20produced%20on%20the%20political%20assembly-line%2C%20or%20the%20chief%20minister%20would%20have%20been%20sent%20packing%20long%20ago.%20Instead%2C%20the%20man%20is%20cosseted%20by%20the%20Centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Nuh%2C%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20communal%20violence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Ebrought%20on%20by%20numerous%20provocative%20and%20violent%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20took%20a%20grave%20turn%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20when%20the%20victims%20began%20to%20be%20punished%2C%20with%20their%20homes%20and%20businesses%20bulldozed%20in%20wanton%20fashion.%20The%20sorry%20spectacle%20ended%20only%20when%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20asked%20if%20the%20state%20government%20was%20intent%20on%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20high%20court%20before%20has%20raised%20such%20a%20question%20about%20a%20state%20government.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20Union%20governmenthas%20not%20seen%20it%20fit%20to%20intervene.%20In%20the%20ordinary%20course%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20have%20been%20forced%20out%20under%20constitutional%20provisions%20crying%20out%20to%20be%20used.%20Why%20such%20monstrous%20passivity%20by%20the%20Union%2C%20then%3F%20When%20Modi%20campaigns%20for%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-engine%E2%80%9D%20governments%2C%20then%20the%20indictment%20of%20the%20high%20court%20in%20Chandigarh%20is%20also%20that%20of%20the%20regime%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Poison%20Has%20Now%20Reached%20India%E2%80%99s%20Schools%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20UP%2C%20recently%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20commended%20for%20preventing%20a%20possible%20communal%20attack%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fips-prabhakar-chaudhary-transferred-4-hours-lathi-charging-kanwariyas-up-bareilly-2414131-2023-07-31%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20senior%20police%20officer%20was%20transferred%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20within%20hours%20of%20the%20brave%20decision%20he%20took.%20Also%20in%20UP%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520Muzaffarnagar%2520village%252C%2520pressure%2520on%2CAct%25E2%2580%25A6%5C%22%3Ea%20teacher%20instructed%20her%20Hindu%20pupils%20to%20take%20turns%20to%20sla