3ESuch%20a%20dispensation%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20not%20getting%20burnt%2C%20seeks%20to%20rely%20on%20hate%20propaganda%20and%20communal%20consolidation%20in%20order%20to%20come%20back%20electorally.%20The%20trick%20has%20worked%20for%20nine%20years%20principally%20because%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20media%20has%20capitulated.%20It%20has%20been%20subverted%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20and%20calculatedly%20fails%20to%20show%20the%20government%20the%20mirror%20in%20order%20to%20benefit%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20lay%20the%20path%20to%20fascism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20crushed%20under%20financial%2C%20emotional%2C%20psychological%20and%20communal%20burdens%2C%20the%20people%20are%2C%20at%20last%2C%20catching%20on.%20The%20regime%20has%20also%20grown%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20bush%20fires%20burning%20within.%20That%20makes%20it%20extra%20jumpy.%20It%20has%20begun%20to%20see%20ghosts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeverywhere.%20That%20is%20why%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Congress%20party%20or%20the%20INDIA%20combine%20that%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20seeks%20to%20suppress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%E2%80%99s%20case%20stands%20out.%20The%20Union%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20building%20national%20highways%20and%20ports%2C%20who%20has%20enjoyed%20a%20very%20positive%20image%20right%20through%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20nine-year%20misrule%2C%20is%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20hounded%20%E2%80%93%20exposing%20internal%20discords.%20The%20leading%20lights%20of%20the%20regime%20may%20perhaps%20even%20be%20viewing%20him%20as%20the%20locus%20of%20a%20likely%20internal%20challenge%20that%20may%20surface%20and%20are%20taking%20action%20to%20pre-empt%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20former%20BJP%20president%20and%20party%20stalwart%20from%20Nagpur%2C%20where%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20is%20situated%2C%20Gadkari%20was%20first%20removed%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20board%2C%20a%20move%20that%20was%20thought%20to%20have%20emanated%20at%20the%20top.%20Now%2C%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20corruption%20in%20a%20recent%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20report%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20retired%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Girish%20Chandra%20Murmu%20%E2%80%93%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20blue-eyed%20boy%20in%20Gujarat%20who%20was%20subsequently%20brought%20to%20New%20Delhi%20for%20high-end%20jobs.%20Did%20Modi%20fear%20there%20might%20be%20blood%20on%20the%20carpet%20if%20his%20cabinet%20colleague%20was%20not%20sought%20to%20be%20side-stabbed%3F%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20to%20a%20news%20portal%2C%20the%20disaffected%20BJP%20leader%20and%20high-profile%20RSS-backer%2C%20Subramanian%20Swamy%2C%20spoke%20of%20extensive%20discontent%20within%20the%20farmer%20community%20and%20the%20working%20classes%20in%20Modi%20Raj.%20Asked%20to%20evaluate%20the%20rime%20%C2%A0%20minister%20in%20juxtaposition%20to%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20swept%20through%20the%20country%20frontally%20challenging%20Modi%2C%20Swamy%20shot%20back%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20asking%20me%20which%20of%20them%20is%20more%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edusht%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Hindi%2F%20Sanskrit%20word%20dusht%20translates%20to%20wicked%20or%20evil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20dynamite-packed%20evaluation%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20apart%2C%20Swamy%20has%20also%20predicted%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20suffer%20if%20it%20goes%20to%20the%20country%20under%20the%20present%20leader.%20His%20proximity%20to%20the%20RSS%20is%20too%20well%20kn