Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20on%20the%20Gabon%2024%20TV%20channel%20was%20made%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20group%20calling%20itself%20the%20%E2%80%9CCommittee%20for%20the%20Transition%20and%20Restoration%20of%20Institutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20on%20TV%20included%20a%20dozen%20army%20colonels%2C%20members%20of%20the%20elite%20Republican%20Guard%2C%20regular%20soldiers%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20to%20represent%20all%20of%20Gabon%E2%80%99s%20security%20and%20defence%20forces%2C%20the%20officers%20declared%20the%20dissolution%20of%20%E2%80%9Call%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20republic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20cited%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpandora-papers-expose-african-leaders-offshore-secrets%2Fa-59399552%5C%22%3Eirresponsible%2C%20unpredictable%20governance%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20a%20deteriorating%20social%20climate%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20their%20intervention%2C%20aiming%20to%20restore%20peace%20by%20ending%20the%20current%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cborders%20are%20closed%20until%20further%20notice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20military%20coup%20in%20%F0%9F%87%AC%F0%9F%87%A6%20Gabon%20is%20gaining%20HUGE%20amounts%20of%20support%20from%20locals.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdROOOjuEJU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdROOOjuEJU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rev%20Laskaris%20(%40REVMAXXING)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FREVMAXXING%2Fstatus%2F1696794378071605353%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETensions%20high%20since%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20have%20escalated%20following%20Saturday%E2%80%99s%20election%2C%20where%2