ernment%2Fmodi-govt-defensive-over-bihar-caste-survey-changes-affidavit-in-supreme-court%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20government%20filing%20two%20successive%20affidavits%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20stand%20about%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20Union%20government%2C%20in%20paragraph%20five%20of%20its%20first%20affidavit%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2028%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20the%20Centre%20can%20conduct%20a%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20it%20purged%20this%20remark%20in%20another%20affidavit%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20paragraph%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinadvertently%20crept%20in%E2%80%9D%20and%2C%20as%20such%20it%20had%20no%20objection%20against%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20action%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%20with%20INDIA%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20mainly%20those%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20%E2%80%93%20hitting%20out%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20opposition%20leaders%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20continuously%20conspiring%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20Dalits%C2%A0and%20backward%20classes%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh-BJP%20represents%20the%20forces%20that%20have%20perpetrated%20atrocities%20on%20the%20poor%20for%20centuries%20and%20are%20still%20doing%20it.%20The%20poor%20people%20have%20understood%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20machinations%20now.%20They%20are%20determined%20to%20drive%20Modi%20out%20of%20power%20in%202024%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20RJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20told%20this%20writer%20ahead%20of%20leaving%20for%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20is%20playing%20every%20trick%20in%20its%20bag%20to%20impede%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%20I%20appeal%20to%20him%20to%20correct%20his%20anti-poor%20mindset%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20national%20spokesman%20Manoj%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20deputy%20CM%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20conspiracy%20has%20been%20exposed.%20It%E2%80%99s%20utterly%20scared%20now%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Congress%E2%80%99s%20Push%20for%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20a%20Step%20Towards%20Ideological%20Unity%20in%20Opposition%20Ranks%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Push%20for%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20a%20Step%20Towards%20Ideological%20Unity%20in%20Opposition%20Ranks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20worries%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Hindutva%20and%20its%20continuous%20hate%20campaign%20against%20minorities%2C%20what%20has%20benefitted%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20elections%20most%2C%20particularly%202014%20onwards%2C%20is%20the%20shift%20of%20the%20major%20chunk%20of%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20Dalits%20votes%20to%20it%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20comprising%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20report%20in%20the%201990s%20led%20the%20regional%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20to%20have%20complete%20sway%20over%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20or%20OBC%20voters%20who%20broadly%20constituted%20about%2060%25%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20these%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20regional%20parties%20in%20Bihar%20and%20UP%20suffered%20multiple%20splits%20and%20the%20BJP%20eventually%20got%20many%20of%20these%20splinter%20groups%20in%20its%20fold.%20The%20Hindutva%20party%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20relatively%20easy%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20because%20these%20states%20did%20not%20have%20strong%20regional%20parties%20and%20the%20BJP%20was%20locked%20in%20direct%20contest%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20did%20not%20play%20OBC%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20the%20RSS%20cadres%20worked%20meticulously%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20to%20incorporate%20the%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20and%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20fold.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20comparative%20lack%20of%20success%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20indirectly%20benefited%20by%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%20(EBCs)%20and%20Dalits%20voting%20for%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20with%20which%20it%20was%20in%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statistics%20gathered%20by%20a%20CSDS%20survey%20suggests%20that%20only%2017%20%25%20of%20OBCs%20had%20voted%20for%20BJP%20in%201996%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20figures%20largely%20remained%20the%20same%20in%20the%202004%20and%202009%20elections.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%2043%25%20of%20the%20OBC%20votes%20in%20the%202014%20elections.%20The%20Hindutva%20party%E2%80%99s%20OBCs%20vote%20share%20further%20swelled%20with%2048%25%20of%20them%20voting%20for%20it%20in%202019%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20perhaps%20recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20OBCs%20votes%20for%20his%20party%2C%20the%20PM%20announced%20the%20Vishwakarma%20Yojna%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%2C%20his%20last%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20polls.%20The%20scheme%20involves%20giving%20financial%20and%20technological%20help%20to%20ironsmiths%2C%20wood%20workers%2C%20goldsmiths%20and%20others%20engaged%20in%20leather%20and%20aluminium-related%20occupations%20in%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Point%20Is%20That%20There%20Is%20Not%20Enough%20Social%20Justice%2C%20Not%20That%20There%20Is%20Too%20Much%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-caste-census%5C%22%3EThe%20Point%20Is%20That%20There%20Is%20Not%20Enough%20Social%20Justice%2C%20Not%20That%20There%20Is%20Too%20Much%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECaste%20survey%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20backdrop%2C%20the%20caste%20survey%20acts%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20clout%20among%20OBCs%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20to%20the%20fold%20of%20the%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20is%20going%20to%20prove%20a%20watershed%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20All%20the%20states%20must%20adopt%20it.%20The%20Centre%20should%20have%20carried%20out%20the%20caste%20census%20in%202021%20itself%2C%20but%20it%20delayed%20it.%20Now%20the%20time%20has%20lapsed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bihar%20CM%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20INDIA%20meet%20at%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%E2%80%99s%20dumping%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20joining%20the%20grand%20alliance%20in%20August%202022%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20RJD%20and%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20supporting%20it.%20The%20survey%20is%20also%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20carry%20out%20caste%20census%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20It%20has%20also%20led%20to%20Nitish%20cementing%20his%20proximity%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20under%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20Yadav%20has%20suffered%20heavily%20on%20account%20of%20losing%20his%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20votes%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20his%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS-BJP%20is%20known%20to%20have%20caste%20Hindus%20%E2%80%93%20Brahmins%20and%20Banias%20(business%20communities)%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20core%20of%20its%20socio-political%20base.%20The%20RSS%20invariably%20has%20had%20Chitpavans%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sub-caste%20of%20the%20Brahmins%20%E2%80%93%20heading%20it%20ever%20since%20its%20formation%20in%201925.%20The%20upper%20crust%20of%20the%20BJP%20too%20is%20layered%20with%20caste%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20work%20for%20the%20backwards%20and%20marginalised%20sections%20is%20only%20peripheral%20and%20cosmetic%20in%20nature.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20highly%20appreciative%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20and%20has%20continuously%20been%20demanding%20the%20Union%20government%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20at%20the%20national%20level%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20senior%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20and%20professor%20at%20Lucknow%20University%2C%20Sudhir%20Panwar%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20ostensibly%2C%20had%20supported%20Nitish%20when%20he%20had%20moved%20the%20resolution%20for%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20Bihar%20legislature.%20The%20party%20also%20supported%20the%20alliance%20parties%E2%80%99%20representatives%20in%20their%20meeting%20with%20the%20PM%20to%20demand%20a%20caste%20census%20early%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20party%20got%20jittery%20when%20the%20Nitish%20government%20set%20in%20motion%20the%20process.%20Outwardly%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20kept%20speaking%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20but%20the%20saffron%20cadres%20led%20a%20covert%20operation%20to%20ensure%20it%20did%20not%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20Sena%2C%20Akhilesh%20Kumar%20and%20others%20were%20among%20seven%20groups%20and%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20all%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20%E2%80%93%20who%20challenged%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cimperil%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%E2%80%9D%20of%20India.%20The%20Patna%20HC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-the-patna-hc-order-on-bihar-caste-census-revive-the-mandal-magic-of-the-early-1990s%5C%22%3Einitially%20put%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20the%20survey%20but%20later%20allowed%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20RSS%20cadres%20and%20sympathisers%20then%20challenged%20the%20HC%E2%80%99s%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20PMO%20was%2C%20apparently%2C%20exposed%20when%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20questioned%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20on%20August%2021%20and%20said%20that%20the%20government%20would%20file%20an%20affidavit%20to%20that%20effect%20in%20the%20SC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20did%20file%20the%20affidavit%20but%20dithered%20on%20it.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20a%20state%20of%20confusion%20on%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20that%20might%20dominate%20the%20discourse%20of%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693393228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10152506%2F2022_8img10_Aug_2022_PTI08_10_2022_000073B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmodi-caste-census-bihar-nitish-tejashwi-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20contrast%20to%20the%20Modi%20government's%20affidavit%20episode%2C%20the%20Bihar%20parties%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20have%20spoken%20of%20how%20the%20caste%20survey%20can%20change%20politics%20for%20the%20better.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmodi-caste-census-bihar-nitish-tejashwi-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Testing%20the%20State%20of%20Constitutional%20Democracy%20in%20India%20Through%20'Assemblies%20of%20Freedom'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F23122754%2FScreenshot-2023-06-23-at-12.27.26-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20so%20long%20as%20the%20name%20of%20freedom%20was%20respected%20and%20only%20its%20actual%20realization%20prevented%2C%20of%20course%20in%20a%20legal%20way%2C%20the%20constitutional%20existence%20of%20liberty%20remained%20intact%2C%20inviolate%2C%20however%20mortal%20the%20blows%20dealt%20to%20its%20existence%20in%20actual%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20Karl%20Marx%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Eighteenth%20Brumaire%20of%20Louis%20Bonaparte%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20the%20state%20of%20health%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%3F%20Is%20it%20wounded%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceroding%E2%80%9D%2C%20breaking%20down%2C%20breaking%20up%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbacksliding%E2%80%9D%2C%20critical%3F%20How%20can%20we%20know%20whether%20we%20are%20still%20living%20in%20a%20constitutional%20democratic%20system%20constituted%20by%20our%20consent%3F%20Is%20there%20still%20a%20constitution%20of%20India%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20questions%20for%20which%20we%20should%20take%20responsibility%20and%20act%20in%20politics%20according%20to%20the%20ratio%20between%20the%20answers%20received%20and%20what%20they%20reveal%20about%20the%20future%20of%20India.%20These%20essential%20questions%20cannot%20be%20answered%20through%20the%20newer%20phrases%20borrowed%20from%20the%20international%20media%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9Cerosion%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbacksliding%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%20meant%20as%20%E2%80%9Call%20the%20perfumes%20of%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20can%20check%20the%20liveliness%20of%20our%20constitutional%20democracy%20only%20by%20testing%20the%20constitution%20through%20thoughtful%20political%20acts.%20Of%20these%20tests%2C%20the%20most%20important%20ones%20for%20this%20situation%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efreedoms%20of%20association%20and%20assembly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Further%2C%20if%20these%20freedoms%20are%20opposed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fbhima-koregaon-violence-sambhaji-bhide-milind-ekbote-hindutva-leaders%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20upper%20caste%20supremacist%20militias%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-riots-2020-crime-branch-reward-to-identify-police-faizan-anthem%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20police%2C%20which%20is%20at%20times%20indistinguishable%20from%20such%20militias%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20we%20should%20urgently%20seek%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20judiciary%3A%20Are%20we%20still%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20your%20honours%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20physicians%20of%20democracy%2C%20we%20administer%20these%20tests%20while%20granting%20our%20assent%20to%20constitutional%20democracy.%20Without%20the%20manifestation%20of%20such%20tests%20of%20freedoms%2C%20the%20constitution%20is%20a%20crumbling%20parchment%20written%20in%20an%20indecipherable%20script.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWho%20is%20opposed%20to%20constitutional%20democracy%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20there%20effectively%20is%20no%20freedom%20of%20association%20and%20assembly%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20position%20in%20India.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20supremacist%20organisation%20of%20the%20minority%20upper%20castes%20(less%20than%2010%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India)%2C%20and%20its%20(conveniently%20disavowable)%20offshoots%20are%20at%20liberty%20to%20violate%20all%20constitutional%20and%20international%20norms%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fcrime%2Fnuh-haryana-bajrang-dal-communal-violence-arrest-muslim-youth%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20take%20out%20armed%20processions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunali