hours%20and%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20her%20dreams.%20We%20are%20so%20proud%20of%20her.%20Her%20journey%20is%20extraordinary%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mehnaaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%2C%20Lilyma%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20handing%20the%20vegetarian%20section%20of%20the%20restaurant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20journey%20started%20there%20in%202012.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20at%203-4%20restaurants%20after%20that%20and%20am%20a%20Head%20chef%20today.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20thanks%20to%20Chef%20Julia%2C%20Jamshed%2C%20Jatin%20and%20Sajeev%20who%20mentored%20me%20at%20the%20restaurants%20I%20worked%20at.%20They%20taught%20me%20everything.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20how%20to%20make%20a%20sandwich%20then%2C%20but%20today%20I%20cook%20a%20fabulous%20risotto%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Lilyma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Sadeev%20Pasricha%2C%20who%20has%20trained%20Lilyma%2C%20has%20known%20her%20for%20eight%20years.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20amazes%20me%20with%20everything%20that%20she%20does.%20She%20is%20very%20diligent%20and%20works%20well%20under%20pressure.%20She%E2%80%99s%20had%20a%20hard%20life%20and%20suffers%20from%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder%20(PTSD).%20We%20help%20her%20channelise%20her%20feelings%20in%20a%20positive%20way.%20She%20is%20a%20quick%20learner%20and%20works%20very%20hard%2C%20for%20almost%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sadeev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Lilyma%20also%20leads%20a%20team%20of%2035%20people%20at%20Dear%20Donna.%20With%20a%20hint%20of%20pride%20in%20her%20voice%2C%20she%20says%20that%20she%20stays%20at%20her%20own%20house%20today%2C%20and%20has%20purchased%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302115%2Fdelhi-doctors-and-volunteers-give-free-healthcare-to-poor-people-on-streets-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20land%20in%20Noida%20and%20Ghaziabad%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt