eir%20interest%20increases%20and%20they%20come%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20We%20already%20know%20that%20the%20dropout%20rate%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20faced%20by%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20in%20the%20government%20school%20because%20when%20they%20are%20educated%20there%20in%20a%20better%20way%20they%20would%20not%20require%20tutoring.%20But%20my%20father%20was%20so%20angry%20at%20my%20decision%20that%20he%20stopped%20speaking%20to%20me.%20If%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20bedroom%2C%20he%20would%20move%20to%20the%20drawing-room%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20continued%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20no%20one%20should%20quit%20on%20their%20dreams.%20Dreams%20have%20the%20power%20to%20become%20reality.%20This%20kept%20me%20motivated%20when%20my%20father%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20me.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20took%20a%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20we%20invited%20former%20vice%20president%20M%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%20for%20a%20project%20launch%2C%20my%20father%20also%20joined%20us%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20understood%20that%20I%20was%20serious%20about%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.