rrange%20meetings%20with%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20engage%20them%20in%20discussions%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20opportunities%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20It%20helps%20build%20enthusiasm%20and%20commitment%20among%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20ensure%20their%20active%20involvement%20in%20the%20implementation%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collaborating%20with%20schools%2C%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20electronic%20devices%2C%20content%2C%20and%20training%20to%20teachers.%20We%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20performance%20of%20children%20in%20Maths%20and%20Science%20because%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20subject%20teachers%20in%20the%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fg0HA2PbezIc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20Dreams%20also%20uses%20a%20third%20party%20Tic%20Tac%20Learning%20app%E2%80%99s%20unique%20%E2%80%9Ctic-tac%E2%80%9D%20learning%20module%2C%20wherein%20they%20animate%20pictures%20and%20high-quality%20video%20content%20aligned%20with%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus.%20With%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20subjects%20like%20Science%20and%20Math%2C%20all%20chapters%20and%20exercises%20are%20converted%20into%20animated%20videos%20in%20Hindi.%20Fo