0foodpharmer)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20embarking%20on%20this%20journey%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20cushy%20job%20that%20paid%20him%20crores%20every%20year%2C%20he%20recalls.%20But%20the%20experiences%20he%20had%20had%20growing%20up%20pushed%20him%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20early%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20discuss%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20he%20recounts%20an%20anecdote%20%E2%80%94%20his%20grandparents%20would%20always%20start%20their%20day%20with%20a%20steaming%20cup%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20two%20biscuits.%20%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20no%20one%20thinks%20about%20the%20ingredients%20present%20in%20these%20biscuits%2C%20or%20how%20much%20sugar%20or%20maida%20they%20might%20contain.%20Most%20biscuits%20in%20the%20market%20also%20have%20palm%20oil.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20once-in-a-week%20chocolate%20that%E2%80%99s%20making%20you%20unhealthy%2C%20but%20actually%20are%20the%20daily%20biscuits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cognisance%20of%20this%20undetected%20evil%20encouraged%20Revant%20to%20pursue%20a%20course%20in%20nutrition%20from%20the%20Institute%20of%20Integrative%20Nutrition%20alongside%20his%20management%20degree%20from%20the%20NYU%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20solving%20business%20problems%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%2C%20%5Bbut%5D%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20same%20skills%20to%20solve%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20problems%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20health.%20The%20blatant%20lies%20used%20by%20food%20companies%20in%20their%20packaging%20really%20bothers%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20this%20passion%20that%20led%20him%20to%20create%20the%20infamous%20viral%20video%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20label%20on%20that%20drink%20says%20that%20you%20get%20stronger%20bones%20and%20muscles.%20The%20reason%20I%20chose